83/** Wrapper for data that needs to be cached.
84 * The cached data can be accessed via the get() method from multiple threads.
85 * The first thread that calls get() will trigger creation of the data item via
86 * the creator method, blocking other threads until the item is available in the cache.
87 * @tparam T the type of the data item in the cache.
88 * @tparam TOwner the class containing the cached item.
89 * @tparam creator the method of TOwner to call in order to create the data item to be cached.
90 */
91template<typename T, typename TOwner, T(TOwner::*creator)() const>
92class CachedItem
93{
94 public:
95 /** Returns a reference to the cached data.
96 * Conceptually this is a const method, i.e. it will always return the same data
97 * The first time it is called, the owner will be asked to create the data.
98 */
99 T &get(const TOwner *owner) const
100 {
101 // create a lambda function to create the cached data
102 auto creatorFunc = [this,owner]() { m_item = (owner->*creator)(); };
103 // use std::call_once to let one thread invoke the creator func
104 std::call_once(m_cache_flag, creatorFunc);
105 // return the cached results
106 return m_item;
107 }
108 private:
109 mutable std::once_flag m_cache_flag; // flag to keep track if the item is already cached
110 mutable T m_item; // the cached data item
111};

115/** Class representing a mapping of properties and the corresponding getter function.
116 * The map should be initialized at initialization time.
117 */
118template<class T>
119class PropertyMap
120{
121 public:
122 using Map = std::map< std::string, TemplateVariant(T::*)() const >;
123
124 PropertyMap(std::initializer_list<typename Map::value_type> init)
125 : m_map(init) {}
126
127 TemplateVariant get(const T *obj,const QCString &n) const
128 {
129 auto it = m_map.find(n.str());
130 return it!=m_map.end() ? (obj->*(it->second))() : TemplateVariant();
131 }
132 StringVector fields() const
133 {
134 StringVector result;
135 result.reserve(m_map.size());
136 for (const auto &imap : m_map) result.push_back(imap.first);
137 return result;
138 }
139
140 Map &map() { return m_map; }
141
142 private:
143 const Map m_map;
144};

148/** @brief Template List iterator support */
149class GenericConstIterator : public TemplateListIntf::ConstIterator
150{
151 public:
152 GenericConstIterator(const TemplateVariantList &list) : m_list(list) {}
153 void toFirst()
154 {
155 m_index=0;
156 }
157 void toLast()
158 {
159 m_index=static_cast<int>(m_list.size())-1;
160 }
161 void toNext()
162 {
163 if (m_index < static_cast<int>(m_list.size())) ++m_index;
164 }
165 void toPrev()
166 {
167 if (m_index>=0) --m_index;
168 }
169 bool current(TemplateVariant &v) const
170 {
171 if (m_index>=0 && m_index < static_cast<int>(m_list.size()))
172 {
173 v = m_list[m_index];
174 return true;
175 }
176 else
177 {
178 v = TemplateVariant();
179 return false;
180 }
181 }
182 private:
183 const TemplateVariantList &m_list;
184 int m_index=0;
185};

189/** @brief standard template list implementation */
190class GenericNodeListContext : public TemplateListIntf
191{
192 public:
193 GenericNodeListContext()
194 {
195 }
196 static TemplateListIntfPtr alloc()
197 {
198 return std::static_pointer_cast<TemplateListIntf>(std::make_shared<GenericNodeListContext>());
199 }
200
201 // TemplateListIntf methods
202 size_t count() const
203 {
204 return m_children.size();
205 }
206 TemplateVariant at(size_t index) const
207 {
208 TemplateVariant result;
209 if (index<count())
210 {
211 result = m_children[index];
212 }
213 return result;
214 }
215 TemplateListIntf::ConstIteratorPtr createIterator() const
216 {
217 return std::make_unique<GenericConstIterator>(m_children);
218 }
219
220 void append(const TemplateVariant &ctn)
221 {
222 m_children.emplace_back(ctn);
223 }
224 bool isEmpty() const
225 {
226 return m_children.empty();
227 }
228 private:
229 std::vector< TemplateVariant > m_children;
230};

234//%% struct Config : configuration options
235//%% {
236class ConfigContext::Private
237{
238 public:
239 // TemplateStructIntf methods
240 StringVector fields() const
241 {
242 return m_fields.get(this);
243 }
244 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &name) const
245 {
246 auto &data = m_configData.get(this);
247 auto it = data.find(name.str());
248 return (it!=data.end()) ? it->second : TemplateVariant();
249 }
250 private:
251 using ConfigData = std::map<std::string,TemplateVariant>;
252
253 ConfigData createConfigData() const
254 {
255 std::map<std::string,TemplateVariant> map;
256 for (auto name : ConfigValues::instance().fields())
257 {
258 const ConfigValues::Info *option = ConfigValues::instance().get(QCString(name));
259 if (option)
260 {
261 switch (option->type)
262 {
263 case ConfigValues::Info::Bool:
264 {
265 bool b = ConfigValues::instance().*(option->value.b);
266 map.insert(std::make_pair(name,TemplateVariant(b)));
267 }
268 break;
269 case ConfigValues::Info::Int:
270 {
271 int i = ConfigValues::instance().*(option->value.i);
272 map.insert(std::make_pair(name,TemplateVariant(i)));
273 }
274 break;
275 case ConfigValues::Info::String:
276 {
277 QCString s = ConfigValues::instance().*(option->value.s);
278 map.insert(std::make_pair(name,TemplateVariant(s)));
279 }
280 break;
281 case ConfigValues::Info::List:
282 {
283 auto fetchList = [](const StringVector &list) -> TemplateVariant
284 {
285 TemplateVariantList elements;
286 elements.reserve(list.size());
287 for (const auto &s : list)
288 {
289 elements.push_back(TemplateVariant(s));
290 }
291 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(elements);
292 };
293 const StringVector &l = ConfigValues::instance().*(option->value.l);
294 map.insert(std::make_pair(name,fetchList(l)));
295 }
296 break;
297 default:
298 break;
299 }
300 }
301 }
302 return map;
303 }
304
305 StringVector createFields() const
306 {
307 return ConfigValues::instance().fields();
308 }
309
310 CachedItem<StringVector, Private, &Private::createFields > m_fields;
311 CachedItem<ConfigData, Private, &Private::createConfigData> m_configData;
312};
313//%% }
314
315ConfigContext::ConfigContext() : p(std::make_unique<Private>())
316{
317}
318
319ConfigContext::~ConfigContext()
320{
321}
322
323TemplateVariant ConfigContext::get(const QCString &name) const
324{
325 return p->get(name);
326}
327
328StringVector ConfigContext::fields() const
329{
330 return p->fields();
331}

335class DoxygenContext::Private
336{
337 public:
338 // TemplateStructIntf methods
339 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
340 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
341
342 private:
343 // Property getters
344 TemplateVariant version() const { return getDoxygenVersion(); }
345 TemplateVariant date() const { return dateToString(DateTimeType::DateTime); }
346 TemplateVariant mathJaxCodeFile() const { return m_mathJaxCodeFile.get(this); }
347 TemplateVariant mathJaxMacros() const { return m_mathJaxMacros.get(this); }
348
349 private:
350 QCString createMathJaxCodeFile() const { return fileToString(Config_getString(MATHJAX_CODEFILE)); }
351 QCString createMathJaxMacros() const { return HtmlGenerator::getMathJaxMacros(); }
352 CachedItem<QCString, Private, &Private::createMathJaxCodeFile> m_mathJaxCodeFile;
353 CachedItem<QCString, Private, &Private::createMathJaxMacros> m_mathJaxMacros;
354 static const PropertyMap<DoxygenContext::Private> s_inst;
355};

392class TranslateContext::Private
393{
394 public:
395
396 Private()
397 {
398 m_javaOpt = Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_JAVA);
399 m_fortranOpt = Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_FOR_FORTRAN);
400 m_vhdlOpt = Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_VHDL);
401 m_sliceOpt = Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_SLICE);
402 }
403
404 // TemplateStructIntf methods
405 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
406 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
407 private:
408
409 // Handlers for properties with parameters
410 TemplateVariant handleGeneratedAt(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
411 {
412 if (args.size()==2)
413 {
414 return theTranslator->trGeneratedAt(args[0].toString(),args[1].toString());
415 }
416 else
417 {
418 err("tr.generateAt should take two arguments, got %zu!\n",args.size());
419 }
420 return TemplateVariant();
421 }
422 TemplateVariant handleInheritanceDiagramFor(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
423 {
424 if (args.size()==1)
425 {
426 return theTranslator->trClassDiagram(args[0].toString());
427 }
428 else
429 {
430 err("tr.inheritanceDiagramFor should take one argument, got %zu!\n",args.size());
431 }
432 return TemplateVariant();
433 }
434 TemplateVariant handleCollaborationDiagramFor(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
435 {
436 if (args.size()==1)
437 {
438 return theTranslator->trCollaborationDiagram(args[0].toString());
439 }
440 else
441 {
442 err("tr.collaborationDiagramFor should take one argument, got %zu!\n",args.size());
443 }
444 return TemplateVariant();
445 }
446 TemplateVariant handleDirDependencyGraphFor(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
447 {
448 if (args.size()==1)
449 {
450 return theTranslator->trDirDepGraph(args[0].toString());
451 }
452 else
453 {
454 err("tr.dirDependencyGraphFor should take one argument, got %zu!\n",args.size());
455 }
456 return TemplateVariant();
457 }
458 TemplateVariant handleInheritsList(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
459 {
460 if (args.size()==1)
461 {
462 return theTranslator->trInheritsList(args[0].toInt());
463 }
464 else
465 {
466 err("tr.inheritsList should take one integer argument, got %zu!\n",args.size());
467 }
468 return TemplateVariant();
469 }
470 TemplateVariant handleInheritedByList(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
471 {
472 if (args.size()==1)
473 {
474 return theTranslator->trInheritedByList(args[0].toInt());
475 }
476 else
477 {
478 err("tr.inheritedByList should take one integer argument, got %zu!\n",args.size());
479 }
480 return TemplateVariant();
481 }
482 TemplateVariant handleWriteList(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
483 {
484 if (args.size()==1)
485 {
486 return theTranslator->trWriteList(args[0].toInt());
487 }
488 else
489 {
490 err("tr.*List should take one integer argument, got %zu!\n",args.size());
491 }
492 return TemplateVariant();
493 }
494 TemplateVariant handleImplementedBy(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
495 {
496 if (args.size()==1)
497 {
498 return theTranslator->trImplementedInList(args[0].toInt());
499 }
500 else
501 {
502 err("tr.implementedBy should take one integer argument, got %zu!\n",args.size());
503 }
504 return TemplateVariant();
505 }
506 TemplateVariant handleReimplementedBy(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
507 {
508 if (args.size()==1)
509 {
510 return theTranslator->trReimplementedInList(args[0].toInt());
511 }
512 else
513 {
514 err("tr.reimplementedBy should take one integer argument, got %zu!\n",args.size());
515 }
516 return TemplateVariant();
517 }
518 TemplateVariant handleSourceRefs(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
519 {
520 if (args.size()==1)
521 {
522 return theTranslator->trReferences()+" "+theTranslator->trWriteList(args[0].toInt())+".";
523 }
524 else
525 {
526 err("tr.sourceRefs should take one integer argument, got %zu\n",args.size());
527 }
528 return TemplateVariant();
529 }
530 TemplateVariant handleSourceRefBys(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
531 {
532 if (args.size()==1)
533 {
534 return theTranslator->trReferencedBy()+" "+theTranslator->trWriteList(args[0].toInt())+".";
535 }
536 else
537 {
538 err("tr.sourceRefBys should take one integer argument, got %zu\n",args.size());
539 }
540 return TemplateVariant();
541 }
542 TemplateVariant handleIncludeDependencyGraph(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
543 {
544 if (args.size()==1)
545 {
546 return theTranslator->trInclDepGraph(args[0].toString());
547 }
548 else
549 {
550 err("tr.includeDependencyGraph should take one string argument, got %zu\n",args.size());
551 }
552 return TemplateVariant();
553 }

873 }

909 }

913 }

915 {

917 bool vhdlOpt = Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_VHDL);
918 return fortranOpt ? theTranslator->trSubprograms() :
919 vhdlOpt ? theTranslator->trFunctionAndProc() :
920 theTranslator->trFunctions();
921 }

1014};

1239//------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1240
1241static TemplateVariant parseDoc(const Definition *def,const QCString &file,int line,
1242 const QCString &relPath,const QCString &docStr,bool isBrief)
1243{
1244 TemplateVariant result;
1245 auto parser { createDocParser() };
1246 auto ast { validatingParseDoc(*parser.get(),file,line,def,0,docStr,TRUE,FALSE,
1247 QCString(),isBrief,FALSE,Config_getBool(MARKDOWN_SUPPORT))
1248 };
1249 const DocNodeAST *astImpl = dynamic_cast<DocNodeAST*>(ast.get());
1250 if (astImpl)
1251 {
1252 TextStream ts;
1253 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
1254 {
1255 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
1256 {
1257 HtmlCodeGenerator codeGen(ts,relPath);
1258 HtmlDocVisitor visitor(ts,codeGen,def);
1259 std::visit(visitor,astImpl->root);
1260 }
1261 break;
1262 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
1263 {
1264 LatexCodeGenerator codeGen(ts,relPath,file);
1265 LatexDocVisitor visitor(ts,codeGen,def->getDefFileExtension());
1266 std::visit(visitor,astImpl->root);
1267 }
1268 break;
1269 // TODO: support other generators
1270 default:
1271 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
1272 break;
1273 }
1274 bool isEmpty = astImpl->isEmpty();
1275 if (isEmpty)
1276 result = "";
1277 else
1278 result = TemplateVariant(ts.str().c_str(),TRUE);
1279 }
1280 return result;
1281}
1282
1283static TemplateVariant parseCode(const Definition *d,const QCString &scopeName,const QCString &relPath,
1284 const QCString &code,int startLine=-1,int endLine=-1,bool showLineNumbers=FALSE)
1285{
1286 auto intf = Doxygen::parserManager->getCodeParser(d->getDefFileExtension());
1287 intf->resetCodeParserState();
1288 TextStream t;
1289 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
1290 {
1291 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
1292 {
1293 HtmlCodeGenerator codeGen(t,relPath);
1294 intf->parseCode(codeGen,scopeName,code,d->getLanguage(),FALSE,QCString(),d->getBodyDef(),
1295 startLine,endLine,TRUE,toMemberDef(d),showLineNumbers,d);
1296 }
1297 break;
1298 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
1299 {
1300 LatexCodeGenerator codeGen(t,relPath,d->docFile());
1301 intf->parseCode(codeGen,scopeName,code,d->getLanguage(),FALSE,QCString(),d->getBodyDef(),
1302 startLine,endLine,TRUE,toMemberDef(d),showLineNumbers,d);
1303 }
1304 break;
1305 // TODO: support other generators
1306 default:
1307 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
1308 break;
1309 }
1310 return TemplateVariant(t.str(),TRUE);
1311}
1312
1313static TemplateVariant parseCode(const FileDef *fd,const QCString &relPath)
1314{
1315 bool filterSourceFiles = Config_getBool(FILTER_SOURCE_FILES);
1316 auto intf = Doxygen::parserManager->getCodeParser(fd->getDefFileExtension());
1317 intf->resetCodeParserState();
1318 TextStream t;
1319 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
1320 {
1321 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
1322 {
1323 HtmlCodeGenerator codeGen(t,relPath);
1324 intf->parseCode(codeGen,QCString(),
1325 fileToString(fd->absFilePath(),filterSourceFiles,TRUE), // the sources
1326 fd->getLanguage(), // lang
1327 FALSE, // isExampleBlock
1328 QCString(), // exampleName
1329 const_cast<FileDef*>(fd), // fileDef, TODO: should be const
1330 -1, // startLine
1331 -1, // endLine
1332 FALSE, // inlineFragment
1333 0, // memberDef
1334 TRUE, // showLineNumbers
1335 0, // searchCtx
1336 TRUE // collectXRefs, TODO: should become FALSE
1337 );
1338 }
1339 break;
1340 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
1341 {
1342 LatexCodeGenerator codeGen(t,relPath,fd->docFile());
1343 intf->parseCode(codeGen,QCString(),
1344 fileToString(fd->absFilePath(),filterSourceFiles,TRUE), // the sources
1345 fd->getLanguage(), // lang
1346 FALSE, // isExampleBlock
1347 QCString(), // exampleName
1348 const_cast<FileDef*>(fd), // fileDef, TODO: should be const
1349 -1, // startLine
1350 -1, // endLine
1351 FALSE, // inlineFragment
1352 0, // memberDef
1353 TRUE, // showLineNumbers
1354 0, // searchCtx
1355 TRUE // collectXRefs, TODO: should become FALSE
1356 );
1357 }
1358 break;
1359 // TODO: support other generators
1360 default:
1361 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
1362 break;
1363 }
1364 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
1365}
1366
1367//------------------------------------------------------------------------
1368
1369template<typename T>
1370class DefinitionContext
1371{
1372 public:
1373 DefinitionContext(const Definition *d) : m_def(d)
1374 {
1375 assert(d!=0);
1376
1377 if (m_def && !m_def->getSourceFileBase().isEmpty())
1378 {
1379 TemplateStructIntfPtr lineLink = TemplateImmutableStruct::alloc(
1380 {
1381 { "text", TemplateVariant(m_def->getStartBodyLine()) },
1382 { "isLinkable", TemplateVariant(TRUE) },
1383 { "fileName", TemplateVariant(m_def->getSourceFileBase()) },
1384 { "anchor", TemplateVariant(m_def->getSourceAnchor()) },
1385 { "isReference", TemplateVariant(FALSE) },
1386 { "externalReference", TemplateVariant("") }
1387 });
1388
1389 QCString text = m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeFile ? m_def->name() :
1390 m_def->getBodyDef() ? m_def->getBodyDef()->name() :
1391 m_def->displayName(TRUE);
1392
1393 TemplateStructIntfPtr fileLink = TemplateImmutableStruct::alloc(
1394 {
1395 { "text", TemplateVariant(text) },
1396 { "isLinkable", TemplateVariant(TRUE) },
1397 { "fileName", TemplateVariant(m_def->getSourceFileBase()) },
1398 { "anchor", TemplateVariant("") },
1399 { "isReference", TemplateVariant(FALSE) },
1400 { "externalReference", TemplateVariant("") }
1401 });
1402
1403 m_sourceDef = TemplateImmutableList::alloc( { lineLink, fileLink });
1404 }
1405 else
1406 {
1407 m_sourceDef = TemplateImmutableList::alloc( {} );
1408 }
1409 }
1410 virtual ~DefinitionContext() = default;
1411
1412 protected:
1413 // Property getters
1414 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return m_def->getOutputFileBase(); }
1415 TemplateVariant anchor() const { return m_def->anchor(); }
1416 TemplateVariant sourceFileName() const { return m_def->getSourceFileBase(); }
1417 TemplateVariant isLinkable() const { return m_def->isLinkable(); }
1418 TemplateVariant isLinkableInProject() const { return m_def->isLinkableInProject(); }
1419 TemplateVariant name() const { return m_def->displayName(TRUE); }
1420 TemplateVariant bareName() const { return m_def->displayName(FALSE); }
1421 TemplateVariant details() const { return m_cachable.details.get(this); }
1422 TemplateVariant brief() const { return m_cachable.brief.get(this); }
1423 TemplateVariant inbodyDocs() const { return m_cachable.inbodyDocs.get(this); }
1424 TemplateVariant dynSectionId() const { return g_globals.dynSectionId; }
1425 TemplateVariant sourceDef() const { return std::static_pointer_cast<TemplateListIntf>(m_sourceDef); }
1426 TemplateVariant navigationPath() const { return m_cachable.navPath.get(this); }
1427 TemplateVariant partOfGroups() const { return m_cachable.partOfGroups.get(this); }
1428 TemplateVariant isReference() const { return m_def->isReference(); }
1429 TemplateVariant externalReference() const { return m_def->externalReference(relPathAsString()); }
1430 TemplateVariant language() const
1431 {
1432 SrcLangExt lang = m_def->getLanguage();
1433 QCString result = "unknown";
1434 switch (lang)
1435 {
1436 case SrcLangExt_Unknown: break;
1437 case SrcLangExt_IDL: result="idl"; break;
1438 case SrcLangExt_Java: result="java"; break;
1439 case SrcLangExt_CSharp: result="csharp"; break;
1440 case SrcLangExt_D: result="d"; break;
1441 case SrcLangExt_PHP: result="php"; break;
1442 case SrcLangExt_ObjC: result="objc"; break;
1443 case SrcLangExt_Cpp: result="cpp"; break;
1444 case SrcLangExt_JS: result="js"; break;
1445 case SrcLangExt_Python: result="python"; break;
1446 case SrcLangExt_Fortran: result="fortran"; break;
1447 case SrcLangExt_VHDL: result="vhdl"; break;
1448 case SrcLangExt_XML: result="xml"; break;
1449 case SrcLangExt_SQL: result="sql"; break;
1450 case SrcLangExt_Markdown: result="markdown"; break;
1451 case SrcLangExt_Slice: result="slice"; break;
1452 case SrcLangExt_Lex: result="lex"; break;
1453 }
1454 return result;
1455 }
1456 TemplateVariant compoundKind() const
1457 {
1458 QCString result = "unspecified";
1459 switch (m_def->definitionType())
1460 {
1461 case Definition::TypeClass: result="class"; break;
1462 case Definition::TypeFile: result="file"; break;
1463 case Definition::TypeNamespace: result="namespace"; break;
1464 case Definition::TypeGroup: result="module"; break;
1465 case Definition::TypePackage: result="package"; break;
1466 case Definition::TypePage: result="page"; break;
1467 case Definition::TypeDir: result="dir"; break;
1468 case Definition::TypeConcept: result="concept"; break;
1469 case Definition::TypeMember: break;
1470 }
1471 return result;
1472 }
1473
1474 protected:
1475
1476 QCString relPathAsString() const
1477 {
1478 bool createSubdirs = Config_getBool(CREATE_SUBDIRS);
1479 return createSubdirs ? QCString("../../") : QCString("");
1480 }
1481 virtual TemplateVariant relPath() const { return relPathAsString(); }
1482
1483
1484 private:
1485
1486 TemplateVariant createDetails() const
1487 {
1488 return TemplateVariant(parseDoc(m_def,m_def->docFile(),m_def->docLine(),
1489 relPathAsString(),m_def->documentation(),FALSE));
1490 }
1491 TemplateVariant createBrief() const
1492 {
1493 if (m_def->hasBriefDescription())
1494 {
1495 return TemplateVariant(parseDoc(m_def,m_def->briefFile(),m_def->briefLine(),
1496 relPathAsString(),m_def->briefDescription(),TRUE));
1497 }
1498 else
1499 {
1500 return TemplateVariant("");
1501 }
1502 }
1503 TemplateVariant createInbodyDocs() const
1504 {
1505 if (!m_def->inbodyDocumentation().isEmpty())
1506 {
1507 return TemplateVariant(parseDoc(m_def,m_def->inbodyFile(),m_def->inbodyLine(),
1508 relPathAsString(),m_def->inbodyDocumentation(),FALSE));
1509 }
1510 else
1511 {
1512 return TemplateVariant("");
1513 }
1514 }
1515 void fillPath(const Definition *def,TemplateVariantList &list) const
1516 {
1517 const Definition *outerScope = def->getOuterScope();
1518 Definition::DefType type = def->definitionType();
1519 if (outerScope && outerScope!=Doxygen::globalScope)
1520 {
1521 fillPath(outerScope,list);
1522 }
1523 else if (type==Definition::TypeFile && (toFileDef(def))->getDirDef())
1524 {
1525 fillPath((toFileDef(def))->getDirDef(),list);
1526 }
1527 list.push_back(NavPathElemContext::alloc(def));
1528 }
1529 TemplateListIntfPtr createNavigationPath() const
1530 {
1531 TemplateVariantList list;
1532 if (m_def->getOuterScope() && m_def->getOuterScope()!=Doxygen::globalScope)
1533 {
1534 fillPath(m_def,list);
1535 }
1536 else if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeFile && (toFileDef(m_def))->getDirDef())
1537 {
1538 fillPath((toFileDef(m_def))->getDirDef(),list);
1539 }
1540 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
1541 }
1542 TemplateListIntfPtr createPartOfGroups() const
1543 {
1544 TemplateVariantList list;
1545 list.reserve(m_def->partOfGroups().size());
1546 for (const auto &gd : m_def->partOfGroups())
1547 {
1548 list.push_back(ModuleContext::alloc(gd));
1549 }
1550 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
1551 }
1552
1553 protected:
1554 struct Cachable
1555 {
1556 using DC = DefinitionContext<T>;
1557 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, DC, &DC::createDetails> details;
1558 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, DC, &DC::createBrief> brief;
1559 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, DC, &DC::createInbodyDocs> inbodyDocs;
1560 CachedItem<TemplateListIntfPtr, DC, &DC::createNavigationPath> navPath;
1561 CachedItem<TemplateListIntfPtr, DC, &DC::createPartOfGroups> partOfGroups;
1562 };
1563
1564 private:
1565 Cachable m_cachable;
1566 const Definition *m_def;
1567 TemplateListIntfPtr m_sourceDef;

1569};

1598class IncludeInfoContext::Private
1599{
1600 public:
1601 Private(const IncludeInfo *info,SrcLangExt lang) :
1602 m_info(info),
1603 m_lang(lang)
1604 {
1605 }
1606 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const
1607 {
1608 return s_inst.get(this,n);
1609 }
1610 StringVector fields() const
1611 {
1612 return s_inst.fields();
1613 }
1614 TemplateVariant isLocal() const
1615 {
1616 bool isIDLorJava = m_lang==SrcLangExt_IDL || m_lang==SrcLangExt_Java;
1617 return m_info->local || isIDLorJava;
1618 }
1619 TemplateVariant isImport() const
1620 {
1621 return m_info->imported || m_lang==SrcLangExt_ObjC;
1622 }
1623 TemplateVariant file() const
1624 {
1625 return m_fileContext.get(this);
1626 }
1627 TemplateVariant name() const
1628 {
1629 return m_info->includeName;
1630 }
1631 private:
1632 const IncludeInfo *m_info;
1633 TemplateVariant createFileContext() const
1634 {
1635 return m_info && m_info->fileDef ?
1636 TemplateVariant(FileContext::alloc(m_info->fileDef)) :
1637 TemplateVariant(false);
1638 }
1639 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createFileContext> m_fileContext;
1640 SrcLangExt m_lang;
1641 static const PropertyMap<IncludeInfoContext::Private> s_inst;
1642};
1643
1644//%% struct IncludeInfo: include file information
1645//%% {

1647 { "file",&Private::file },
1648 { "name",&Private::name },
1649 { "isImport",&Private::isImport },
1650 { "isLocal",&Private::isLocal }
1651};
1652//%% }

1655{
1656}
1657

1659{
1660}

1793
1794 TemplateVariant hasInheritanceDiagram() const
1795 {
1796 bool result=FALSE;
1797 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
1798 auto classGraph = Config_getEnum(CLASS_GRAPH);
1799 bool classGraphEnabled = classGraph==CLASS_GRAPH_t::YES || classGraph==CLASS_GRAPH_t::GRAPH;
1800
1801 if (haveDot && classGraphEnabled)
1802 {
1803 DotClassGraphPtr cg = getClassGraph();
1804 result = !cg->isTrivial() && !cg->isTooBig();
1805 }
1806 else if (classGraphEnabled)
1807 {
1808 result = numInheritanceNodes()>0;
1809 }
1810 return result;
1811 }
1812 TemplateVariant inheritanceDiagram() const
1813 {
1814 TextStream t;
1815 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
1816 auto classGraph = Config_getEnum(CLASS_GRAPH);
1817 bool classGraphEnabled = classGraph==CLASS_GRAPH_t::YES || classGraph==CLASS_GRAPH_t::GRAPH;
1818
1819 if (haveDot && classGraphEnabled)
1820 {
1821 DotClassGraphPtr cg = getClassGraph();
1822 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
1823 {
1824 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
1825 {
1826 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_BITMAP,EOF_Html,
1827 g_globals.outputDir,
1828 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(m_classDef->getOutputFileBase()),
1829 relPathAsString(),TRUE,TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
1830 );
1831 }
1832 break;
1833 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
1834 {
1835 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_EPS,EOF_LaTeX,
1836 g_globals.outputDir,
1837 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+m_classDef->getOutputFileBase()+".tex",
1838 relPathAsString(),TRUE,TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
1839 );
1840 }
1841 break;
1842 // TODO: support other generators
1843 default:
1844 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
1845 break;
1846 }
1847 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
1848 }
1849 else if (classGraphEnabled)
1850 {
1851 ClassDiagram d(m_classDef);
1852 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
1853 {
1854 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
1855 {
1856 TextStream tt;
1857
1858 QCString name = convertToHtml(m_classDef->displayName());
1859 d.writeImage(tt,g_globals.outputDir,
1860 relPathAsString(),
1861 m_classDef->getOutputFileBase());
1862 if (!tt.empty())
1863 {
1864 t << "<div class=\"center\">\n";
1865 t << " <img src=\"";
1866 t << relPathAsString() << m_classDef->getOutputFileBase();
1867 t << ".png\" usemap=\"#" << convertToId(name) << "_map\" alt=\"\"/>\n";
1868 t << " <map id=\"" << convertToId(name) << "_map\" name=\"" << convertToId(name) << "_map\">\n";
1869 t << tt.str();
1870 t << " </map>\n";
1871 t << "</div>";
1872 }
1873 else
1874 {
1875 t << "<div class=\"center\">\n";
1876 t << " <img src=\"";
1877 t << relPathAsString() << m_classDef->getOutputFileBase();
1878 t << ".png\" alt=\"\"/>\n";
1879 t << "</div>";
1880 }
1881 }
1882 break;
1883 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
1884 {
1885 d.writeFigure(t,g_globals.outputDir,m_classDef->getOutputFileBase());
1886 }
1887 break;
1888 // TODO: support other generators
1889 default:
1890 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
1891 break;
1892 }
1893 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
1894 }
1895 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
1896 }
1897 DotClassGraphPtr getCollaborationGraph() const
1898 {
1899 return m_cachable.collaborationGraph.get(this);
1900 }
1901 TemplateVariant hasCollaborationDiagram() const
1902 {
1903 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
1904 return haveDot && !getCollaborationGraph()->isTrivial();
1905 }
1906 TemplateVariant collaborationDiagram() const
1907 {
1908 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
1909 TextStream t;
1910 if (haveDot)
1911 {
1912 DotClassGraphPtr cg = getCollaborationGraph();
1913 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
1914 {
1915 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
1916 {
1917 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_BITMAP,EOF_Html,
1918 g_globals.outputDir,
1919 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(m_classDef->getOutputFileBase()),
1920 relPathAsString(),TRUE,TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
1921 );
1922 }
1923 break;
1924 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
1925 {
1926 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_EPS,EOF_LaTeX,
1927 g_globals.outputDir,
1928 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+m_classDef->getOutputFileBase()+".tex",
1929 relPathAsString(),TRUE,TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
1930 );
1931 }
1932 break;
1933 // TODO: support other generators
1934 default:
1935 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
1936 break;
1937 }
1938 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
1939 }
1940 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
1941 }

1968 TemplateVariant createClasses() const
1969 {
1970 TemplateVariantList classList;
1971 classList.reserve(m_classDef->getClasses().size());
1972 for (const auto &cd : m_classDef->getClasses())
1973 {
1974 if (cd->visibleInParentsDeclList())
1975 {
1976 classList.push_back(ClassContext::alloc(cd));
1977 }
1978 }
1979 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(classList);
1980 }
1981 TemplateVariant createInnerClasses() const
1982 {
1983 TemplateVariantList classList;
1984 classList.reserve(m_classDef->getClasses().size());
1985 for (const auto &cd : m_classDef->getClasses())
1986 {
1987 if (!cd->isAnonymous() &&
1988 cd->isLinkableInProject() &&
1989 cd->isEmbeddedInOuterScope() &&
1990 cd->partOfGroups().empty()
1991 )
1992 {
1993 classList.push_back(ClassContext::alloc(cd));
1994 }
1995 }
1996 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(classList);
1997 }
1998 TemplateVariant createMemberList(MemberListType type,const QCString &title) const
1999 {
2000 const MemberList *ml = m_classDef->getMemberList(type);
2001 return ml ? TemplateVariant(MemberListInfoContext::alloc(m_classDef,relPathAsString(),ml,title,""))
2002 : TemplateVariant(false);

2184 TemplateVariant createExamples() const
2185 {
2186 TemplateVariantList list;
2187 list.reserve(m_classDef->getExamples().size());

2193 {

2198 { "isReference", TemplateVariant(FALSE) },
2199 { "externalReference", TemplateVariant("") }
2200 });
2201 list.push_back(s);
2202 }
2203 }
2204 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
2205 }
2206 void addTemplateDecls(const Definition *d,TemplateVariantList &tl) const
2207 {
2208 if (d->definitionType()==Definition::TypeClass)
2209 {
2210 const Definition *parent = d->getOuterScope();
2211 if (parent)
2212 {
2213 addTemplateDecls(parent,tl);
2214 }
2215 const ClassDef *cd=toClassDef(d);
2216 if (!cd->templateArguments().empty())
2217 {
2218 TemplateListIntfPtr al = ArgumentListContext::alloc(cd->templateArguments(),cd,relPathAsString());
2219 // since a TemplateVariant does take ownership of the object, we add it
2220 // a separate list just to be able to delete it and avoid a memory leak
2221 tl.push_back(al);
2222 }
2223 }
2224 }
2225 TemplateVariant createTemplateDecls() const
2226 {
2227 TemplateVariantList tl;
2228 addTemplateDecls(m_classDef,tl);
2229 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(tl);
2230 }
2231 TemplateVariant createAdditionalInheritedMembers() const
2232 {
2233 TemplateListIntfPtr list = InheritedMemberInfoListContext::alloc();
2234 auto ctx = std::dynamic_pointer_cast<InheritedMemberInfoListContext>(list);
2235 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_pubTypes,theTranslator->trPublicTypes());
2236 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_services,theTranslator->trServices());
2237 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_interfaces,theTranslator->trInterfaces());
2238 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_pubSlots,theTranslator->trPublicSlots());
2239 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_signals,theTranslator->trSignals());
2240 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_pubMethods,
2241 m_classDef->getLanguage()==SrcLangExt_ObjC ? theTranslator->trInstanceMethods()
2242 : theTranslator->trPublicMembers());
2243 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_pubStaticMethods,

2250 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_proMethods,theTranslator->trProtectedMembers());
2251 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_proStaticMethods,theTranslator->trStaticProtectedMembers());
2252 ctx->addMemberList(m_classDef,MemberListType_proAttribs,theTranslator->trProtectedAttribs());

2280 }
2281 }

2493class NamespaceContext::Private : public DefinitionContext<NamespaceContext::Private>
2494{
2495 public:
2496 Private(const NamespaceDef *nd) : DefinitionContext<NamespaceContext::Private>(nd),
2497 m_namespaceDef(nd)
2498 {
2499 }
2500
2501 // TemplateStructIntf methods
2502 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
2503 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
2504
2505 private:
2506 // Property getters
2507 TemplateVariant title() const { return TemplateVariant(m_namespaceDef->title()); }
2508 TemplateVariant highlight() const { return TemplateVariant("namespaces"); }
2509 TemplateVariant subHighlight() const { return TemplateVariant(""); }
2510 TemplateVariant compoundType() const { return m_namespaceDef->compoundTypeString(); }
2511 TemplateVariant hasDetails() const { return m_namespaceDef->hasDetailedDescription(); }
2512 TemplateVariant classes() const { return m_cachable.classes.get(this); }
2513 TemplateVariant namespaces() const { return m_cachable.namespaces.get(this); }
2514 TemplateVariant constantgroups() const { return m_cachable.constantgroups.get(this); }
2515 TemplateVariant typedefs() const { return m_cachable.typedefs.get(this); }
2516 TemplateVariant sequences() const { return m_cachable.sequences.get(this); }
2517 TemplateVariant dictionaries() const { return m_cachable.dictionaries.get(this); }
2518 TemplateVariant enums() const { return m_cachable.enums.get(this); }
2519 TemplateVariant functions() const { return m_cachable.functions.get(this); }
2520 TemplateVariant variables() const { return m_cachable.variables.get(this); }
2521 TemplateVariant memberGroups() const { return m_cachable.memberGroups.get(this); }
2522 TemplateVariant detailedTypedefs() const { return m_cachable.detailedTypedefs.get(this); }
2523 TemplateVariant detailedSequences() const { return m_cachable.detailedSequences.get(this); }
2524 TemplateVariant detailedDictionaries() const { return m_cachable.detailedDictionaries.get(this); }
2525 TemplateVariant detailedEnums() const { return m_cachable.detailedEnums.get(this); }
2526 TemplateVariant detailedFunctions() const { return m_cachable.detailedFunctions.get(this); }
2527 TemplateVariant detailedVariables() const { return m_cachable.detailedVariables.get(this); }
2528 TemplateVariant inlineClasses() const { return m_cachable.inlineClasses.get(this); }
2529
2530 private:
2531 TemplateVariant createClasses() const
2532 {
2533 bool sliceOpt = Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_SLICE);
2534 TemplateVariantList classList;
2535 classList.reserve(m_namespaceDef->getClasses().size());
2536 for (const auto &cd : m_namespaceDef->getClasses())
2537 {
2538 if (sliceOpt && (cd->compoundType()==ClassDef::Struct ||
2539 cd->compoundType()==ClassDef::Interface ||
2540 cd->compoundType()==ClassDef::Exception))
2541 {
2542 continue; // These types appear in their own sections.
2543 }
2544 if (cd->visibleInParentsDeclList())
2545 {
2546 classList.push_back(ClassContext::alloc(cd));
2547 }
2548 }
2549 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(classList);
2550 }
2551 TemplateVariant createNamespaces() const
2552 {
2553 TemplateVariantList list;
2554 list.reserve(m_namespaceDef->getNamespaces().size());
2555 for (const auto &nd : m_namespaceDef->getNamespaces())
2556 {
2557 if (nd->isLinkable() && !nd->isConstantGroup())
2558 {
2559 list.push_back(NamespaceContext::alloc(nd));
2560 }
2561 }
2562 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
2563 }
2564 TemplateVariant createConstantgroups() const
2565 {
2566 TemplateVariantList list;
2567 list.reserve(m_namespaceDef->getNamespaces().size());
2568 for (const auto &nd : m_namespaceDef->getNamespaces())
2569 {
2570 if (nd->isLinkable() && nd->isConstantGroup())
2571 {
2572 list.push_back(NamespaceContext::alloc(nd));
2573 }
2574 }
2575 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
2576 }
2577 TemplateVariant createMemberList(MemberListType type,const QCString &title) const
2578 {
2579 const MemberList *ml = m_namespaceDef->getMemberList(type);
2580 return ml ? TemplateVariant(MemberListInfoContext::alloc(m_namespaceDef,relPathAsString(),ml,title,""))
2581 : TemplateVariant(false);
2582 }
2583 TemplateVariant createTypedefs() const
2584 {
2585 return createMemberList(MemberListType_decTypedefMembers,theTranslator->trTypedefs());
2586 }
2587 TemplateVariant createSequences() const
2588 {
2589 return createMemberList(MemberListType_decSequenceMembers,theTranslator->trSequences());
2590 }
2591 TemplateVariant createDictionaries() const
2592 {
2593 return createMemberList(MemberListType_decDictionaryMembers,theTranslator->trDictionaries());
2594 }
2595 TemplateVariant createEnums() const
2596 {
2597 return createMemberList(MemberListType_decEnumMembers,theTranslator->trEnumerations());
2598 }
2599 TemplateVariant createFunctions() const
2600 {
2601 SrcLangExt lang = m_namespaceDef->getLanguage();
2602 return createMemberList(MemberListType_decFuncMembers,lang==SrcLangExt_Fortran ? theTranslator->trSubprograms() :
2603 lang==SrcLangExt_VHDL ? theTranslator->trFunctionAndProc() :
2604 theTranslator->trFunctions());
2605 }
2606 TemplateVariant createVariables() const
2607 {
2608 bool sliceOpt = Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_SLICE);
2609 return createMemberList(MemberListType_decVarMembers, sliceOpt ? theTranslator->trConstants() :
2610 theTranslator->trVariables());
2611 }
2612 TemplateVariant createDetailedTypedefs() const
2613 {
2614 return createMemberList(MemberListType_docTypedefMembers,theTranslator->trTypedefDocumentation());
2615 }
2616 TemplateVariant createDetailedSequences() const
2617 {
2618 return createMemberList(MemberListType_docSequenceMembers,theTranslator->trSequenceDocumentation());
2619 }
2620 TemplateVariant createDetailedDictionaries() const
2621 {
2622 return createMemberList(MemberListType_docDictionaryMembers,theTranslator->trDictionaryDocumentation());
2623 }
2624 TemplateVariant createDetailedEnums() const
2625 {
2626 return createMemberList(MemberListType_docEnumMembers,theTranslator->trEnumerationTypeDocumentation());
2627 }
2628 TemplateVariant createDetailedFunctions() const
2629 {
2630 SrcLangExt lang = m_namespaceDef->getLanguage();
2631 return createMemberList(MemberListType_docFuncMembers, lang==SrcLangExt_Fortran ? theTranslator->trSubprogramDocumentation() :
2632 theTranslator->trFunctionDocumentation());
2633 }
2634 TemplateVariant createDetailedVariables() const
2635 {
2636 bool sliceOpt = Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_SLICE);
2637 return createMemberList(MemberListType_docVarMembers, sliceOpt ? theTranslator->trConstantDocumentation() :
2638 theTranslator->trVariableDocumentation());
2639 }
2640 TemplateVariant createMemberGroups() const
2641 {
2642 return !m_namespaceDef->getMemberGroups().empty() ?
2643 MemberGroupListContext::alloc(m_namespaceDef,relPathAsString(),
2644 m_namespaceDef->getMemberGroups(),
2645 m_namespaceDef->subGrouping()) :
2646 MemberGroupListContext::alloc();
2647 }
2648 TemplateVariant createInlineClasses() const
2649 {
2650 TemplateVariantList list;
2651 list.reserve(m_namespaceDef->getClasses().size());
2652 for (const auto &cd : m_namespaceDef->getClasses())
2653 {
2654 if (!cd->isAnonymous() &&
2655 cd->isLinkableInProject() &&
2656 cd->isEmbeddedInOuterScope() &&
2657 cd->partOfGroups().empty())
2658 {
2659 list.push_back(ClassContext::alloc(cd));
2660 }
2661 }
2662 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
2663 }
2664
2665 const NamespaceDef *m_namespaceDef;
2666 struct Cachable : public DefinitionContext<NamespaceContext::Private>::Cachable
2667 {
2668 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createClasses> classes;
2669 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createNamespaces> namespaces;

2671 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createTypedefs> typedefs;
2672 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createSequences> sequences;
2673 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDictionaries> dictionaries;
2674 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createEnums> enums;
2675 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createFunctions> functions;
2676 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createVariables> variables;
2677 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createMemberGroups> memberGroups;
2678 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDetailedTypedefs> detailedTypedefs;
2679 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDetailedSequences> detailedSequences;
2680 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDetailedDictionaries> detailedDictionaries;
2681 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDetailedEnums> detailedEnums;
2682 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDetailedFunctions> detailedFunctions;
2683 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDetailedVariables> detailedVariables;
2684 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createInlineClasses> inlineClasses;

2783
2784 TemplateVariant hasIncludeGraph() const
2785 {
2786 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
2787 DotInclDepGraphPtr incGraph = getIncludeGraph();
2788 return (haveDot && !incGraph->isTooBig() && !incGraph->isTrivial());
2789 }
2790 TemplateVariant includeGraph() const
2791 {
2792 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
2793 TextStream t;
2794 if (haveDot)
2795 {
2796 DotInclDepGraphPtr cg = getIncludeGraph();
2797 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
2798 {
2799 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
2800 {
2801 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_BITMAP,EOF_Html,
2802 g_globals.outputDir,
2803 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(m_fileDef->getOutputFileBase()),
2804 relPathAsString(),TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
2805 );
2806 }
2807 break;
2808 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
2809 {
2810 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_EPS,EOF_LaTeX,
2811 g_globals.outputDir,
2812 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+m_fileDef->getOutputFileBase()+".tex",
2813 relPathAsString(),TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
2814 );
2815 }
2816 break;
2817 // TODO: support other generators
2818 default:
2819 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
2820 break;
2821 }
2822 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
2823 }
2824 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
2825 }
2826 TemplateVariant hasIncludedByGraph() const
2827 {
2828 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
2829 DotInclDepGraphPtr incGraph = getIncludedByGraph();
2830 return (haveDot && !incGraph->isTooBig() && !incGraph->isTrivial());
2831 }
2832 TemplateVariant includedByGraph() const
2833 {
2834 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
2835 TextStream t;
2836 if (haveDot)
2837 {
2838 DotInclDepGraphPtr cg = getIncludedByGraph();
2839 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
2840 {
2841 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
2842 {
2843 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_BITMAP,EOF_Html,
2844 g_globals.outputDir,
2845 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(m_fileDef->getOutputFileBase()),
2846 relPathAsString(),TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
2847 );
2848 }
2849 break;
2850 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
2851 {
2852 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_EPS,EOF_LaTeX,
2853 g_globals.outputDir,
2854 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+m_fileDef->getOutputFileBase()+".tex",
2855 relPathAsString(),TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
2856 );
2857 }
2858 break;
2859 // TODO: support other generators
2860 default:
2861 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
2862 break;
2863 }
2864 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
2865 }
2866 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
2867 }

2900 }

2913 }

2960 lang==SrcLangExt_VHDL ? theTranslator->trFunctionAndProc() :

2990 {
2991 SrcLangExt lang = m_fileDef->getLanguage();
2992 return createMemberList(MemberListType_docFuncMembers, lang==SrcLangExt_Fortran ? theTranslator->trSubprogramDocumentation() :
2993 theTranslator->trFunctionDocumentation());

2998 }
2999 TemplateVariant createMemberGroups() const
3000 {
3001 return !m_fileDef->getMemberGroups().empty() ?
3002 MemberGroupListContext::alloc(m_fileDef,relPathAsString(),m_fileDef->getMemberGroups(),m_fileDef->subGrouping()) :
3003 MemberGroupListContext::alloc();
3004 }
3005 TemplateVariant createInlineClasses() const
3006 {
3007 TemplateVariantList list;
3008 list.reserve(m_fileDef->getClasses().size());
3009 for (const auto &cd : m_fileDef->getClasses())
3010 {
3011 if (!cd->isAnonymous() &&
3012 cd->isLinkableInProject() &&
3013 cd->isEmbeddedInOuterScope() &&
3014 cd->partOfGroups().empty())
3015 {
3016 list.push_back(ClassContext::alloc(cd));
3017 }
3018 }
3019 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
3020 }

3138 TemplateVariant hasDirGraph() const
3139 {
3140 bool result=FALSE;
3141 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
3142 bool dirGraph = Config_getBool(DIRECTORY_GRAPH);
3143 if (haveDot && dirGraph)
3144 {
3145 DotDirDepsPtr graph = getDirDepsGraph();
3146 result = !graph->isTrivial();
3147 }
3148 return result;
3149 }
3150 TemplateVariant dirGraph() const
3151 {
3152 TextStream t;
3153 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
3154 bool dirGraph = Config_getBool(DIRECTORY_GRAPH);
3155 if (haveDot && dirGraph)
3156 {
3157 DotDirDepsPtr graph = getDirDepsGraph();
3158 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
3159 {
3160 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
3161 {
3162 graph->writeGraph(t,GOF_BITMAP,
3163 EOF_Html,
3164 g_globals.outputDir,
3165 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(m_dirDef->getOutputFileBase()),
3166 relPathAsString(),
3167 TRUE,
3168 g_globals.dynSectionId,
3169 FALSE);
3170 }
3171 break;
3172 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
3173 {
3174 graph->writeGraph(t,GOF_EPS,
3175 EOF_LaTeX,
3176 g_globals.outputDir,
3177 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+m_dirDef->getOutputFileBase()+".tex",
3178 relPathAsString(),
3179 TRUE,
3180 g_globals.dynSectionId,
3181 FALSE);
3182 }
3183 break;
3184 // TODO: support other generators
3185 default:
3186 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
3187 break;
3188 }
3189 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
3190 }
3191 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
3192 }

3269class PageContext::Private : public DefinitionContext<PageContext::Private>
3270{
3271 public:
3272 Private(const PageDef *pd,bool isMainPage,bool isExample)
3273 : DefinitionContext<PageContext::Private>(pd) , m_pageDef(pd), m_isMainPage(isMainPage),
3274 m_isExample(isExample)
3275 {
3276 }
3277
3278 // TemplateStructIntf methods
3279 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
3280 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
3281
3282 // Property getters
3283 TemplateVariant title() const
3284 {
3285 if (m_isMainPage)
3286 {
3287 QCString projectName = Config_getString(PROJECT_NAME);
3288 if (Doxygen::mainPage && !Doxygen::mainPage->title().isEmpty())
3289 {
3290 if (Doxygen::mainPage->title().lower()!="notitle")
3291 {
3292 return m_pageDef->title();
3293 }
3294 else
3295 {
3296 return "";
3297 }
3298 }
3299 else if (!projectName.isEmpty())
3300 {
3301 return projectName+" "+theTranslator->trDocumentation();
3302 }
3303 else
3304 {
3305 return theTranslator->trMainPage();
3306 }
3307 }
3308 else if (m_isExample)
3309 {
3310 return m_pageDef->name();
3311 }
3312 else
3313 {
3314 return m_pageDef->title();
3315 }
3316 }
3317 TemplateVariant relPath() const
3318 {
3319 return m_isMainPage ? TemplateVariant("") :
3320 TemplateVariant(DefinitionContext<PageContext::Private>::relPath());
3321 }
3322 TemplateVariant highlight() const
3323 {
3324 if (m_isMainPage)
3325 {
3326 return "main";
3327 }
3328 else
3329 {
3330 return "pages";
3331 }
3332 }
3333 TemplateVariant subHighlight() const
3334 {
3335 return "";
3336 }
3337 TemplateVariant example() const
3338 {
3339 return m_cachable.example.get(this);
3340 }
3341 private:
3342 TemplateVariant createExample() const
3343 {
3344 return m_isExample ?
3345 TemplateVariant(parseDoc(m_pageDef,m_pageDef->docFile(),m_pageDef->docLine(),
3346 relPathAsString(),"\\include "+m_pageDef->name(),FALSE)) :
3347 TemplateVariant("");
3348 }
3349
3350 const PageDef *m_pageDef;
3351 struct Cachable : public DefinitionContext<PageContext::Private>::Cachable
3352 {
3353 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createExample> example;
3354 };
3355 Cachable m_cachable;
3356 bool m_isMainPage;
3357 bool m_isExample;
3358 static const PropertyMap<PageContext::Private> s_inst;
3359};

3391
3392class TextGeneratorHtml : public TextGeneratorIntf
3393{
3394 public:
3395 TextGeneratorHtml(TextStream &ts,const QCString &relPath)
3396 : m_ts(ts), m_relPath(relPath) {}
3397 void writeString(const QCString &s,bool keepSpaces) const
3398 {
3399 static const char *hex="0123456789ABCDEF";
3400 if (s.isEmpty()) return;
3401 if (keepSpaces)
3402 {
3403 const char *p=s.data();
3404 char c;
3405 while ((c=*p++))
3406 {
3407 switch(c)
3408 {
3409 case '<': m_ts << "&lt;"; break;
3410 case '>': m_ts << "&gt;"; break;
3411 case '\'': m_ts << "&#39;"; break;
3412 case '"': m_ts << "&quot;"; break;
3413 case '&': m_ts << "&amp;"; break;
3414 case ' ': m_ts << "&#160;"; break;
3415 default:
3416 {
3417 uchar uc = static_cast<uchar>(c);
3418 if (uc<32 && !isspace(c)) // non-printable control characters
3419 {
3420 m_ts << "&#x24" << hex[uc>>4] << hex[uc&0xF] << ";";
3421 }
3422 else
3423 {
3424 m_ts << c;
3425 }
3426 }
3427 break;
3428 }
3429 }
3430 }
3431 else
3432 {
3433 m_ts << convertToHtml(s);
3434 }
3435 }
3436
3437 void writeBreak(int indent) const
3438 {
3439 m_ts << "<br />";
3440 for (int i=0;i<indent;i++)
3441 {
3442 m_ts << "&#160;";
3443 }
3444 }
3445
3446 void writeLink(const QCString &ref,const QCString &f,
3447 const QCString &anchor,const QCString &name
3448 ) const
3449 {
3450 if (!ref.isEmpty())
3451 {
3452 m_ts << "<a class=\"elRef\" ";
3453 m_ts << externalLinkTarget();
3454 }
3455 else
3456 {
3457 m_ts << "<a class=\"el\" ";
3458 }
3459 m_ts << "href=\"";
3460 m_ts << externalRef(m_relPath,ref,TRUE);
3461 if (!f.isEmpty()) m_ts << addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(f);
3462 if (!anchor.isEmpty()) m_ts << "#" << anchor;
3463 m_ts << "\">";
3464 m_ts << convertToHtml(name);
3465 m_ts << "</a>";
3466 }
3467
3468 private:
3469 TextStream &m_ts;
3470 QCString m_relPath;
3471};
3472
3473//------------------------------------------------------------------------
3474
3475class TextGeneratorLatex : public TextGeneratorIntf
3476{
3477 public:
3478 TextGeneratorLatex(TextStream &ts) : m_ts(ts) {}
3479 void writeString(const QCString &s,bool keepSpaces) const
3480 {
3481 if (s==0) return;
3482 m_ts << convertToLaTeX(s,FALSE,keepSpaces);
3483 }
3484 void writeBreak(int indent) const
3485 {
3486 m_ts << "\\\\*\n";
3487 for (int i=0;i<indent;i++)
3488 {
3489 m_ts << "~";
3490 }
3491 }
3492 void writeLink(const QCString &ref,const QCString &f,
3493 const QCString &anchor,const QCString &text
3494 ) const
3495 {
3496 bool pdfHyperlinks = Config_getBool(PDF_HYPERLINKS);
3497 if (ref.isEmpty() && pdfHyperlinks)
3498 {
3499 m_ts << "\\mbox{\\hyperlink{";
3500 if (!f.isEmpty()) m_ts << stripPath(f);
3501 if (!f.isEmpty() && !anchor.isEmpty()) m_ts << "_";
3502 if (!anchor.isEmpty()) m_ts << anchor;
3503 m_ts << "}{";
3504 filterLatexString(m_ts,text,
3505 false, // insideTabbing
3506 false, // insidePre
3507 false, // insideItem
3508 false, // insideTable
3509 false // keepSpaces
3510 );
3511 m_ts << "}}";
3512 }
3513 else
3514 {
3515 m_ts << "\\textbf{ ";
3516 filterLatexString(m_ts,text,
3517 false, // insideTabbing
3518 false, // insidePre
3519 false, // insideItem
3520 false, // insideTable
3521 false // keepSpaces
3522 );
3523 m_ts << "}";
3524 }
3525 }
3526
3527 private:
3528 TextStream &m_ts;
3529};
3530
3531//------------------------------------------------------------------------
3532
3533class TextGeneratorFactory
3534{
3535 public:
3536 static TextGeneratorFactory *instance()
3537 {
3538 static TextGeneratorFactory *instance = new TextGeneratorFactory;
3539 return instance;
3540 }
3541 TextGeneratorIntf *create(TextStream &ts,const QCString &relPath)
3542 {
3543 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
3544 {
3545 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
3546 return new TextGeneratorHtml(ts,relPath);
3547 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
3548 return new TextGeneratorLatex(ts);
3549 default:
3550 break;
3551 }
3552 return 0;
3553 }
3554 private:
3555 TextGeneratorFactory() = default;
3556 virtual ~TextGeneratorFactory() = default;
3557};
3558
3559TemplateVariant createLinkedText(const Definition *def,const QCString &relPath,const QCString &text)
3560{
3561 TextStream ts;
3562 TextGeneratorIntf *tg = TextGeneratorFactory::instance()->create(ts,relPath);
3563 if (tg)
3564 {
3565 linkifyText(*tg,def->getOuterScope(),def->getBodyDef(),def,text);
3566 delete tg;
3567 return TemplateVariant(ts.str().c_str(),true);
3568 }
3569 else
3570 {
3571 return text;
3572 }
3573}

3710 TemplateVariant functionQualifier() const
3711 {
3712 if (!m_memberDef->isObjCMethod() &&
3713 (m_memberDef->isFunction() || m_memberDef->isSlot() ||
3714 m_memberDef->isPrototype() || m_memberDef->isSignal()
3715 )
3716 )
3717 {
3718 return "()";
3719 }
3720 else
3721 {
3722 return "";
3723 }
3724 }
3725 TemplateVariant hasCallGraph() const
3726 {
3727 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
3728 if (m_memberDef->hasCallGraph() && haveDot &&
3729 (m_memberDef->isFunction() || m_memberDef->isSlot() || m_memberDef->isSignal()))
3730 {
3731 DotCallGraphPtr cg = getCallGraph();
3732 return !cg->isTooBig() && !cg->isTrivial();
3733 }
3734 return TemplateVariant(FALSE);
3735 }
3736 TemplateVariant callGraph() const
3737 {
3738 if (hasCallGraph().toBool())
3739 {
3740 DotCallGraphPtr cg = getCallGraph();
3741 TextStream t;
3742 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
3743 {
3744 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
3745 {
3746 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_BITMAP,EOF_Html,
3747 g_globals.outputDir,
3748 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(m_memberDef->getOutputFileBase()),
3749 relPathAsString(),TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
3750 );
3751 }
3752 break;
3753 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
3754 {
3755 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_EPS,EOF_LaTeX,
3756 g_globals.outputDir,
3757 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+m_memberDef->getOutputFileBase()+".tex",
3758 relPathAsString(),TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
3759 );
3760 }
3761 break;
3762 // TODO: support other generators
3763 default:
3764 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
3765 break;
3766 }
3767 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
3768 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
3769 }
3770 else
3771 {
3772 return TemplateVariant("");
3773 }
3774 }
3775 TemplateVariant referencedByRelation() const
3776 {
3777 if (hasReferencedByRelation().toBool())
3778 {
3779 err("context.cpp: referencedByRelation not yet implemented\n");
3780 }
3781 return TemplateVariant("");

3783 TemplateVariant hasCallerGraph() const

3785 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);

3787 (m_memberDef->isFunction() || m_memberDef->isSlot() || m_memberDef->isSignal()))

3794 TemplateVariant callerGraph() const
3795 {
3796 if (hasCallerGraph().toBool())
3797 {
3798 DotCallGraphPtr cg = getCallerGraph();
3799 TextStream t;
3800 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
3801 {
3802 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
3803 {
3804 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_BITMAP,EOF_Html,
3805 g_globals.outputDir,
3806 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(m_memberDef->getOutputFileBase()),
3807 relPathAsString(),TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
3808 );
3809 }
3810 break;
3811 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
3812 {
3813 cg->writeGraph(t,GOF_EPS,EOF_LaTeX,
3814 g_globals.outputDir,
3815 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+m_memberDef->getOutputFileBase()+".tex",
3816 relPathAsString(),TRUE,g_globals.dynSectionId
3817 );
3818 }
3819 break;
3820 // TODO: support other generators
3821 default:
3822 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
3823 break;
3824 }
3825 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
3826 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
3827 }
3828 else
3829 {
3830 return TemplateVariant("");
3831 }
3832 }
3833 TemplateVariant referencesRelation() const
3834 {
3835 if (hasReferencesRelation().toBool())
3836 {
3837 err("context.cpp: referencesRelation not yet implemented\n");
3838 }
3839 return TemplateVariant("");
3840 }
3841 TemplateVariant handleDetailsVisibleFor(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
3842 {
3843 if (args.size()==1)
3844 {
3845 QCString containerStr = args[0].toString();
3846 MemberListContainer container = MemberListContainer::Class;
3847 if (containerStr=="module") container = MemberListContainer::Group;
3848 else if (containerStr=="file") container = MemberListContainer::File;
3849 else if (containerStr=="namespace") container = MemberListContainer::Namespace;
3850 return m_memberDef->isDetailedSectionVisible(container);
3851 }
3852 else
3853 {
3854 err(".detailsVisibleFor should take one string argument, got %zu\n",args.size());
3855 }
3856 return TemplateVariant();
3857 }
3858 TemplateVariant detailsVisibleFor() const
3859 {
3860 return TemplateVariant(std::bind(&Private::handleDetailsVisibleFor,this,std::placeholders::_1));
3861 }
3862 TemplateVariant handleNameWithContextFor(const TemplateVariantList &args) const
3863 {
3864 if (args.size()==1)
3865 {
3866 SrcLangExt lang = m_memberDef->getLanguage();
3867 QCString n = m_memberDef->name();
3868 QCString ctx = args[0].toString();
3869 QCString sep = getLanguageSpecificSeparator(lang,TRUE);
3870 if (m_memberDef->getEnumScope() && m_memberDef->livesInsideEnum())
3871 {
3872 n.prepend(m_memberDef->getEnumScope()->displayName()+sep);
3873 }
3874 if (ctx=="module" && m_memberDef->getClassDef() && !m_memberDef->isRelated())
3875 {
3876 n.prepend(m_memberDef->getClassDef()->displayName()+sep);
3877 }
3878 else if ((ctx=="module" || ctx=="file") && m_memberDef->getNamespaceDef())
3879 {
3880 n.prepend(m_memberDef->getNamespaceDef()->displayName()+sep);
3881 }
3882 return n;
3883 }
3884 else
3885 {
3886 err(".nameWithContextFor should take one string argument, got %zu\n",args.size());
3887 }
3888 return TemplateVariant();
3889 }
3890 TemplateVariant nameWithContextFor() const
3891 {
3892 return TemplateVariant(std::bind(&Private::handleNameWithContextFor,this,std::placeholders::_1));
3893 }
3894
3895 private:
3896
3897 TemplateVariant createTemplateArgs() const
3898 {
3899 return !m_memberDef->templateArguments().empty() ?
3900 TemplateVariant(ArgumentListContext::alloc(m_memberDef->templateArguments(),m_memberDef,relPathAsString())) :
3901 TemplateVariant(false);
3902 }
3903 TemplateVariant createTemplateAlias() const
3904 {
3905 return m_memberDef->isTypeAlias() ?
3906 TemplateVariant(createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(),
3907 QCString(" = ")+m_memberDef->typeString())) :
3908 TemplateVariant("");
3909 }
3910 TemplateVariant createPropertyAttrs() const
3911 {
3912 TemplateVariantList list;
3913 list.reserve(6);
3914 if (m_memberDef->isProperty())
3915 {
3916 if (m_memberDef->isGettable()) list.push_back("get");
3917 if (m_memberDef->isPrivateGettable()) list.push_back("private get");
3918 if (m_memberDef->isProtectedGettable()) list.push_back("protected get");
3919 if (m_memberDef->isSettable()) list.push_back("set");
3920 if (m_memberDef->isPrivateSettable()) list.push_back("private set");
3921 if (m_memberDef->isProtectedSettable()) list.push_back("protected set");
3922 }
3923 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
3924 }
3925 TemplateVariant createEventAttrs() const
3926 {
3927 TemplateVariantList list;
3928 list.reserve(3);
3929 if (m_memberDef->isEvent())
3930 {
3931 if (m_memberDef->isAddable()) list.push_back("add");
3932 if (m_memberDef->isRemovable()) list.push_back("remove");
3933 if (m_memberDef->isRaisable()) list.push_back("raise");
3934 }
3935 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
3936 }
3937 TemplateVariant createParameters() const
3938 {
3939 const ArgumentList &defArgList = getDefArgList();
3940 return !m_memberDef->isProperty() ?
3941 ArgumentListContext::alloc(defArgList,m_memberDef,relPathAsString()) :
3942 ArgumentListContext::alloc();
3943 }
3944 TemplateVariant createEnumValues() const
3945 {
3946 return m_memberDef->isEnumerate() ?
3947 TemplateVariant(MemberListContext::alloc(m_memberDef->enumFieldList())) :
3948 TemplateVariant(false);
3949 }
3950 TemplateVariant createFileDef() const
3951 {
3952 return m_memberDef->getFileDef() ?
3953 TemplateVariant(FileContext::alloc(m_memberDef->getFileDef())) :
3954 TemplateVariant(false);
3955 }
3956 TemplateVariant createNamespaceDef() const
3957 {
3958 return m_memberDef->getNamespaceDef() ?
3959 TemplateVariant(NamespaceContext::alloc(m_memberDef->getNamespaceDef())) :
3960 TemplateVariant(false);
3961 }
3962 TemplateVariant createClassDef() const
3963 {
3964 return m_memberDef->getClassDef() ?
3965 TemplateVariant(ClassContext::alloc(m_memberDef->getClassDef())) :
3966 TemplateVariant(false);
3967 }
3968 TemplateVariant createCategory() const
3969 {
3970 return m_memberDef->category() ?
3971 TemplateVariant(ClassContext::alloc(m_memberDef->category())) :
3972 TemplateVariant(false);
3973 }
3974 TemplateVariant createCategoryRelation() const
3975 {
3976 return m_memberDef->categoryRelation() ?
3977 TemplateVariant(MemberContext::alloc(m_memberDef->categoryRelation())) :
3978 TemplateVariant(false);
3979 }
3980 TemplateVariant createDefinition() const
3981 {
3982 return createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(),
3983 m_memberDef->displayDefinition());
3984 }
3985 TemplateVariant createTrailingReturnType() const
3986 {
3987 const ArgumentList &al = getDefArgList();
3988 return !al.trailingReturnType().isEmpty() ?
3989 TemplateVariant(createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(), al.trailingReturnType())) :
3990 TemplateVariant("");
3991 }
3992 TemplateVariant createTemplateDecls() const
3993 {
3994 TemplateVariantList list;
3995 const ClassDef *cd=m_memberDef->getClassDef();
3996 if (!m_memberDef->definitionTemplateParameterLists().empty())
3997 {
3998 for (const ArgumentList &tal : m_memberDef->definitionTemplateParameterLists())
3999 {
4000 if (!tal.empty())
4001 {
4002 list.push_back(ArgumentListContext::alloc(tal,m_memberDef,relPathAsString()));
4003 }
4004 }
4005 }
4006 else
4007 {
4008 if (cd && !m_memberDef->isRelated() && !m_memberDef->isTemplateSpecialization())
4009 {
4010 for (const ArgumentList &tal : cd->getTemplateParameterLists())
4011 {
4012 if (!tal.empty())
4013 {
4014 list.push_back(ArgumentListContext::alloc(tal,m_memberDef,relPathAsString()));
4015 }
4016 }
4017 }
4018 if (!m_memberDef->templateArguments().empty()) // function template prefix
4019 {
4020 list.push_back(ArgumentListContext::alloc(
4021 m_memberDef->templateArguments(),m_memberDef,relPathAsString()));
4022 }
4023 }
4024 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
4025 }
4026 TemplateVariant createAnonymousType() const
4027 {
4028 const ClassDef *cd = m_memberDef->getClassDefOfAnonymousType();
4029 return cd ? TemplateVariant(ClassContext::alloc(cd)) : TemplateVariant(false);
4030 }
4031 TemplateVariant createParamDocs() const
4032 {
4033 if (m_memberDef->argumentList().hasDocumentation())
4034 {
4035 QCString paramDocs;
4036 for (const Argument &a : m_memberDef->argumentList())
4037 {
4038 if (a.hasDocumentation())
4039 {
4040 QCString docs = a.docs;
4041 QCString direction = extractDirection(docs);
4042 paramDocs+="@param"+direction+" "+a.name+" "+docs;
4043 }
4044 }
4045 return TemplateVariant(parseDoc(m_memberDef,
4046 m_memberDef->docFile(),m_memberDef->docLine(),
4047 relPathAsString(),paramDocs,FALSE));
4048 }
4049 return TemplateVariant("");
4050 }
4051 TemplateVariant createImplements() const
4052 {
4053 const MemberDef *md = m_memberDef->reimplements();
4054 TemplateVariantList list;
4055 if (md)
4056 {
4057 const ClassDef *cd = md->getClassDef();
4058 // filter on pure virtual/interface methods
4059 if (cd && (md->virtualness()==Specifier::Pure || cd->compoundType()==ClassDef::Interface))
4060 {
4061 list.push_back(MemberContext::alloc(md));
4062 }
4063 }
4064 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
4065 }
4066 TemplateVariant createReimplements() const
4067 {
4068 const MemberDef *md = m_memberDef->reimplements();
4069 TemplateVariantList list;
4070 if (md)
4071 {
4072 const ClassDef *cd = md->getClassDef();
4073 // filter on non-pure virtual & non interface methods
4074 if (cd && md->virtualness()!=Specifier::Pure && cd->compoundType()!=ClassDef::Interface)
4075 {
4076 list.push_back(MemberContext::alloc(md));
4077 }
4078 }
4079 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
4080 }
4081 TemplateVariant createImplementedBy() const
4082 {
4083 TemplateVariantList list;
4084 list.reserve(m_memberDef->reimplementedBy().size());
4085 for (const auto &md : m_memberDef->reimplementedBy())
4086 {
4087 const ClassDef *cd = md->getClassDef();
4088 // filter on pure virtual/interface methods
4089 if (cd && md->virtualness()==Specifier::Pure && cd->compoundType()==ClassDef::Interface)
4090 {
4091 list.push_back(MemberContext::alloc(md));
4092 }
4093 }
4094 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
4095 }
4096 TemplateVariant createReimplementedBy() const
4097 {
4098 TemplateVariantList list;
4099 list.reserve(m_memberDef->reimplementedBy().size());
4100 for (const auto &md : m_memberDef->reimplementedBy())
4101 {
4102 const ClassDef *cd = md->getClassDef();
4103 // filter on non-pure virtual & non interface methods
4104 if (cd && md->virtualness()!=Specifier::Pure && cd->compoundType()!=ClassDef::Interface)
4105 {
4106 list.push_back(MemberContext::alloc(md));
4107 }
4108 }
4109 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
4110 }
4111 TemplateVariant createExamples() const
4112 {
4113 TemplateVariantList list;
4114 if (m_memberDef->hasExamples())
4115 {
4116 list.reserve(m_memberDef->getExamples().size());
4117 for (const auto &ex : m_memberDef->getExamples())
4118 {
4119 TemplateStructIntfPtr s = TemplateImmutableStruct::alloc(
4120 {
4121 { "text", TemplateVariant(ex.name) },
4122 { "isLinkable", TemplateVariant(TRUE) },
4123 { "anchor", TemplateVariant(ex.anchor) },
4124 { "fileName", TemplateVariant(ex.file) },
4125 { "isReference", TemplateVariant(FALSE) },
4126 { "externalReference",TemplateVariant("") }
4127 });
4128 list.push_back(s);
4129 }
4130 }
4131 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
4132 }
4133 TemplateVariant createSourceRefs() const
4134 {
4135 return MemberListContext::alloc(m_memberDef->getReferencesMembers());
4136 }
4137 TemplateVariant createSourceRefBys() const
4138 {
4139 return MemberListContext::alloc(m_memberDef->getReferencedByMembers());
4140 }
4141 DotCallGraphPtr createCallGraph() const
4142 {
4143 return std::make_shared<DotCallGraph>(m_memberDef,FALSE);
4144 }
4145 DotCallGraphPtr createCallerGraph() const
4146 {
4147 return std::make_shared<DotCallGraph>(m_memberDef,TRUE);
4148 }
4149 TemplateVariant createAnonymousMember() const
4150 {
4151 return m_memberDef->fromAnonymousMember() ?
4152 TemplateVariant(MemberContext::alloc(m_memberDef)) :
4153 TemplateVariant(false);
4154 }
4155 TemplateVariant createLabels() const
4156 {
4157 StringVector sl = m_memberDef->getLabels(m_memberDef->getOuterScope());
4158 TemplateVariantList list;
4159 list.reserve(sl.size());
4160 for (const auto &s : sl)
4161 {
4162 list.push_back(s.c_str());
4163 }
4164 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
4165 }
4166 TemplateVariant createTypeConstraints() const
4167 {
4168 return !m_memberDef->typeConstraints().empty() ?
4169 TemplateVariant(ArgumentListContext::alloc(m_memberDef->typeConstraints(),m_memberDef,relPathAsString())) :
4170 TemplateVariant(ArgumentListContext::alloc());
4171 }
4172 TemplateVariant createInitializerAsCode() const
4173 {
4174 QCString scopeName;
4175 if (m_memberDef->getClassDef())
4176 {
4177 scopeName = m_memberDef->getClassDef()->name();
4178 }
4179 else if (m_memberDef->getNamespaceDef())
4180 {
4181 scopeName = m_memberDef->getNamespaceDef()->name();
4182 }
4183 return TemplateVariant(parseCode(m_memberDef,
4184 scopeName,relPathAsString(),
4185 m_memberDef->initializer()));
4186 }
4187 TemplateVariant createInitializer() const
4188 {
4189 return createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(),m_memberDef->initializer());
4190 }
4191 TemplateVariant createSourceCode() const
4192 {
4193 QCString codeFragment;
4194 const FileDef *fd = m_memberDef->getBodyDef();
4195 int startLine = m_memberDef->getStartBodyLine();
4196 int endLine = m_memberDef->getEndBodyLine();
4197 if (fd && readCodeFragment(fd->absFilePath(),startLine,endLine,codeFragment))
4198 {
4199 QCString scopeName;
4200 if (m_memberDef->getClassDef())
4201 {
4202 scopeName = m_memberDef->getClassDef()->name();
4203 }
4204 else if (m_memberDef->getNamespaceDef())
4205 {
4206 scopeName = m_memberDef->getNamespaceDef()->name();
4207 }
4208 return parseCode(m_memberDef,
4209 scopeName,relPathAsString(),
4210 codeFragment,startLine,endLine,TRUE);
4211 }
4212 return TemplateVariant("");
4213 }
4214 TemplateVariant createDeclType() const
4215 {
4216 return createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(),m_memberDef->getDeclType());
4217 }
4218 TemplateVariant createDeclArgs() const
4219 {
4220 return createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(),m_memberDef->argsString());
4221 }
4222 TemplateVariant createFieldType() const
4223 {
4224 return createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(),m_memberDef->fieldType());
4225 }
4226 TemplateVariant createException() const
4227 {
4228 return createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(),m_memberDef->excpString());
4229 }
4230 TemplateVariant createBitfields() const
4231 {
4232 return createLinkedText(m_memberDef,relPathAsString(),m_memberDef->bitfieldString());
4233 }

4235 const MemberDef *m_memberDef;

4586 DotGroupCollaborationPtr getGroupGraph() const { return m_cachable.groupGraph.get(this); }
4587
4588 TemplateVariant hasGroupGraph() const
4589 {
4590 bool result=FALSE;
4591 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
4592 bool groupGraphs = Config_getBool(GROUP_GRAPHS);
4593 if (haveDot && groupGraphs)
4594 {
4595 DotGroupCollaborationPtr graph = getGroupGraph();
4596 result = !graph->isTrivial();
4597 }
4598 return result;
4599 }
4600 TemplateVariant groupGraph() const
4601 {
4602 TextStream t;
4603 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
4604 bool groupGraphs = Config_getBool(GROUP_GRAPHS);
4605 if (haveDot && groupGraphs)
4606 {
4607 DotGroupCollaborationPtr graph = getGroupGraph();
4608 switch (g_globals.outputFormat)
4609 {
4610 case ContextOutputFormat_Html:
4611 {
4612 graph->writeGraph(t,GOF_BITMAP,
4613 EOF_Html,
4614 g_globals.outputDir,
4615 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+addHtmlExtensionIfMissing(m_groupDef->getOutputFileBase()),
4616 relPathAsString(),
4617 TRUE,
4618 g_globals.dynSectionId);
4619 }
4620 break;
4621 case ContextOutputFormat_Latex:
4622 {
4623 graph->writeGraph(t,GOF_EPS,
4624 EOF_LaTeX,
4625 g_globals.outputDir,
4626 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+m_groupDef->getOutputFileBase()+".tex",
4627 relPathAsString(),
4628 TRUE,
4629 g_globals.dynSectionId);
4630 }
4631 break;
4632 // TODO: support other generators
4633 default:
4634 err("context.cpp: output format not yet supported\n");
4635 break;
4636 }
4637 g_globals.dynSectionId++;
4638 }
4639 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
4640 }

4993//%% list ClassList[Class] : list of classes
4994class ClassListContext::Private : public GenericNodeListContext
4995{
4996 public:
4997 void addClasses(const ClassLinkedMap &classLinkedMap)
4998 {
4999 for (const auto &cd : classLinkedMap)
5000 {
5001 if (cd->getLanguage()==SrcLangExt_VHDL &&
5002 (VhdlDocGen::convert(cd->protection())==VhdlDocGen::PACKAGECLASS ||
5003 VhdlDocGen::convert(cd->protection())==VhdlDocGen::PACKBODYCLASS)
5004 ) // no architecture
5005 {
5006 continue;
5007 }
5008 if (cd->isLinkableInProject() && cd->templateMaster()==0 &&
5009 !cd->isHidden() && !cd->isEmbeddedInOuterScope())
5010 {
5011 append(ClassContext::alloc(cd.get()));
5012 }
5013 }
5014 }
5015};

5018{

5020 p->addClasses(*Doxygen::hiddenClassLinkedMap);
5021}

5045class ClassIndexContext::Private
5046{

5055 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return "classes"; }
5056 TemplateVariant relPath() const { return ""; }
5057 TemplateVariant highlight() const { return "classes"; }
5058 TemplateVariant subhighlight() const { return "classindex"; }
5059 TemplateVariant title() const
5060 {
5061 return Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_FOR_FORTRAN) ? theTranslator->trDataTypes() :
5062 Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_VHDL) ? theTranslator->trDesignUnits() :
5063 theTranslator->trCompoundIndex();
5064 }
5065 private:
5066 TemplateVariant createClasses() const
5067 {
5068 TemplateVariantList list;
5069 list.reserve(Doxygen::classLinkedMap->size());
5070 if (Doxygen::classLinkedMap)
5071 {
5072 for (const auto &cd : *Doxygen::classLinkedMap)
5073 {
5074 if (cd->getLanguage()==SrcLangExt_VHDL &&
5075 (VhdlDocGen::convert(cd->protection())==VhdlDocGen::PACKAGECLASS ||
5076 VhdlDocGen::convert(cd->protection())==VhdlDocGen::PACKBODYCLASS)
5077 ) // no architecture
5078 {
5079 continue;
5080 }
5081 if (cd->isLinkableInProject() && cd->templateMaster()==0)
5082 {
5083 list.push_back(ClassContext::alloc(cd.get()));
5084 }
5085 }
5086 }
5087 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
5088 }

5091 static const PropertyMap<ClassIndexContext::Private> s_inst;

5126
5127static int computeMaxDepth(const TemplateListIntfPtr list)
5128{
5129 int maxDepth=0;
5130 if (list)
5131 {
5132 TemplateListIntf::ConstIteratorPtr it = list->createIterator();
5133 TemplateVariant v;
5134 for (it->toFirst();it->current(v);it->toNext())
5135 {
5136 const TemplateStructIntfPtr s = v.toStruct();
5137 TemplateVariant child = s->get("children");
5138 int d = computeMaxDepth(child.toList())+1;
5139 if (d>maxDepth) maxDepth=d;
5140 }
5141 }
5142 return maxDepth;
5143}
5144
5145static int computeNumNodesAtLevel(const TemplateStructIntfPtr s,int level,int maxLevel)
5146{
5147 int num=0;
5148 if (level<maxLevel)
5149 {
5150 num++;
5151 TemplateVariant child = s->get("children");
5152 if (child.toList())
5153 {
5154 TemplateListIntf::ConstIteratorPtr it = child.toList()->createIterator();
5155 TemplateVariant v;
5156 for (it->toFirst();it->current(v);it->toNext())
5157 {
5158 num+=computeNumNodesAtLevel(v.toStruct(),level+1,maxLevel);
5159 }
5160 }
5161 }
5162 return num;
5163}
5164
5165static int computePreferredDepth(const TemplateListIntfPtr list,int maxDepth)
5166{
5167 int preferredNumEntries = Config_getInt(HTML_INDEX_NUM_ENTRIES);
5168 int preferredDepth=1;
5169 if (preferredNumEntries>0)
5170 {
5171 int depth = maxDepth;
5172 for (int i=1;i<=depth;i++)
5173 {
5174 int num=0;
5175 TemplateListIntf::ConstIteratorPtr it = list->createIterator();
5176 TemplateVariant v;
5177 for (it->toFirst();it->current(v);it->toNext())
5178 {
5179 num+=computeNumNodesAtLevel(v.toStruct(),0,i);
5180 }
5181 if (num<=preferredNumEntries)
5182 {
5183 preferredDepth=i;
5184 }
5185 else
5186 {
5187 break;
5188 }
5189 }
5190 }
5191 return preferredDepth;
5192}
5193
5194//------------------------------------------------------------------------
5195
5196class ClassHierarchyContext::Private
5197{
5198 public:
5199 Private()
5200 {
5201 m_classTree = NestingContext::alloc(0,ContextTreeType::ClassInheritance,0);
5202 auto ctx = std::dynamic_pointer_cast<NestingContext>(m_classTree);
5203 ClassDefSet visitedClasses;
5204 ctx->addClassHierarchy(*Doxygen::classLinkedMap,visitedClasses);
5205 ctx->addClassHierarchy(*Doxygen::hiddenClassLinkedMap,visitedClasses);
5206 }
5207
5208 // TemplateStructIntf methods
5209 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
5210 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
5211
5212 private:
5213 // Property getters
5214 TemplateVariant tree() const { return TemplateVariant(m_classTree); }
5215 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return "hierarchy"; }
5216 TemplateVariant relPath() const { return ""; }
5217 TemplateVariant highlight() const { return "classes"; }
5218 TemplateVariant subhighlight() const { return "classhierarchy"; }
5219 TemplateVariant diagrams() const { return m_diagrams.get(this); }
5220 TemplateVariant maxDepth() const { return m_maxDepth.get(this); }
5221 TemplateVariant preferredDepth() const { return m_preferredDepth.get(this); }
5222 TemplateVariant title() const
5223 {
5224 return Config_getBool(OPTIMIZE_OUTPUT_VHDL) ? theTranslator->trDesignUnitHierarchy() :
5225 theTranslator->trClassHierarchy();
5226 }
5227 private:
5228 int createMaxDepth() const
5229 {
5230 return computeMaxDepth(m_classTree);
5231 }
5232 int createPreferredDepth() const
5233 {
5234 return computePreferredDepth(m_classTree,m_maxDepth.get(this));
5235 }
5236 TemplateVariant createDiagrams() const
5237 {
5238 TemplateVariantList diagrams;
5239 DotGfxHierarchyTablePtr hierarchy = std::make_shared<DotGfxHierarchyTable>();
5240 diagrams.reserve(hierarchy->subGraphs().size());
5241 int id=0;
5242 for (auto n : hierarchy->subGraphs())
5243 {
5244 diagrams.push_back(InheritanceGraphContext::alloc(hierarchy,n,id++));
5245 }
5246 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(diagrams);
5247 }
5248
5249 TemplateListIntfPtr m_classTree;
5250 CachedItem<int, Private, &Private::createMaxDepth> m_maxDepth;
5251 CachedItem<int, Private, &Private::createPreferredDepth> m_preferredDepth;
5252 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDiagrams> m_diagrams;
5253 static const PropertyMap<ClassHierarchyContext::Private> s_inst;
5254};
5255
5256//%% struct ClassHierarchy: inheritance tree
5257//%% {

5259 { "tree", &Private::tree },
5260 { "fileName", &Private::fileName },
5261 { "relPath", &Private::relPath },
5262 { "highlight", &Private::highlight },
5263 { "subhighlight", &Private::subhighlight },
5264 { "diagrams", &Private::diagrams },
5265 { "maxDepth", &Private::maxDepth },
5266 { "preferredDepth", &Private::preferredDepth },
5267 { "title", &Private::title },
5268};

5277}
