5289//------------------------------------------------------------------------
5290
5291class NestingNodeContext::Private
5292{
5293 public:
5294 Private(const NestingNodeContext *parent,const NestingNodeContext *thisNode,
5295 ContextTreeType type,
5296 const Definition *d,int index,int level,
5297 bool addCls,bool addCps,bool inherit, bool hideSuper,
5298 ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5299 : m_parent(parent), m_type(type), m_def(d), m_level(level), m_index(index)
5300 {
5301 m_children = std::dynamic_pointer_cast<NestingContext>(NestingContext::alloc(thisNode,m_type,level+1));
5302 m_members = std::dynamic_pointer_cast<NestingContext>(NestingContext::alloc(thisNode,m_type,level+1));
5303 addNamespaces(addCls,addCps,visitedClasses);
5304 addClasses(inherit,hideSuper,visitedClasses);
5305 addDirFiles(visitedClasses);
5306 addPages(visitedClasses);
5307 addModules(visitedClasses);
5308 addMembers(visitedClasses);
5309 }
5310
5311 // TemplateStructIntf methods
5312 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
5313 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
5314
5315 TemplateVariant id() const
5316 {
5317 QCString result;
5318 if (m_parent) result=m_parent->id();
5319 result+=QCString().setNum(m_index)+"_";
5320 return result;
5321 }
5322
5323 private:
5324 // Property getters
5325 TemplateVariant isLeafNode() const { return m_children->count()==0; }
5326 TemplateVariant children() const { return std::static_pointer_cast<TemplateListIntf>(m_children); }
5327 TemplateVariant members() const { return std::static_pointer_cast<TemplateListIntf>(m_members); }
5328 TemplateVariant getClass() const { return m_class.get(this); }
5329 TemplateVariant getNamespace() const { return m_namespace.get(this); }
5330 TemplateVariant getDir() const { return m_dir.get(this); }
5331 TemplateVariant getFile() const { return m_file.get(this); }
5332 TemplateVariant getPage() const { return m_page.get(this); }
5333 TemplateVariant getModule() const { return m_module.get(this); }
5334 TemplateVariant getMember() const { return m_member.get(this); }
5335 TemplateVariant level() const { return m_level; }
5336 TemplateVariant brief() const { return m_brief.get(this); }
5337 TemplateVariant isLinkable() const { return m_def->isLinkable(); }
5338 TemplateVariant anchor() const { return m_def->anchor(); }
5339 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return m_def->getOutputFileBase(); }
5340 TemplateVariant isReference() const { return m_def->isReference(); }
5341 TemplateVariant externalReference() const { return m_def->externalReference(relPathAsString()); }
5342 TemplateVariant name() const
5343 {
5344 if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeMember && m_type==ContextTreeType::Module)
5345 {
5346 return toMemberDef(m_def)->qualifiedName();
5347 }
5348 else
5349 {
5350 return m_def->displayName(m_type==ContextTreeType::Module);
5351 }
5352 }
5353 TemplateVariant partOfGroup() const
5354 {
5355 return m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeMember ? toMemberDef(m_def)->getGroupDef()!=0 :
5356 !m_def->partOfGroups().empty();
5357 }
5358 QCString relPathAsString() const
5359 {
5360 bool createSubdirs = Config_getBool(CREATE_SUBDIRS);
5361 return createSubdirs ? QCString("../../") : QCString("");
5362 }
5363
5364 //------------------------------------------------------------------
5365
5366 void addClasses(bool inherit, bool hideSuper,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5367 {
5368 const ClassDef *cd = toClassDef(m_def);
5369 if (cd)
5370 {
5371 if (inherit)
5372 {
5373 bool hasChildren = visitedClasses.find(cd)==visitedClasses.end() &&
5374 !hideSuper && classHasVisibleChildren(cd);
5375 if (hasChildren)
5376 {
5377 visitedClasses.insert(cd);
5378 if (cd->getLanguage()==SrcLangExt_VHDL)
5379 {
5380 m_children->addDerivedClasses(cd->baseClasses(),false,visitedClasses);
5381 }
5382 else
5383 {
5384 m_children->addDerivedClasses(cd->subClasses(),false,visitedClasses);
5385 }
5386 }
5387 }
5388 else
5389 {
5390 m_children->addClasses(cd->getClasses(),FALSE,visitedClasses);
5391 }
5392 }
5393 const GroupDef *gd = toGroupDef(m_def);
5394 if (gd)
5395 {
5396 m_children->addClasses(gd->getClasses(),FALSE,visitedClasses);
5397 }
5398 }
5399 void addConcepts(ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5400 {
5401 const GroupDef *gd = toGroupDef(m_def);
5402 if (gd)
5403 {
5404 m_children->addConcepts(gd->getConcepts(),FALSE,visitedClasses);
5405 }
5406 }
5407 void addNamespaces(bool addClasses,bool addConcepts,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5408 {
5409 const NamespaceDef *nd = toNamespaceDef(m_def);
5410 if (nd)
5411 {
5412 if (!nd->getNamespaces().empty())
5413 {
5414 m_children->addNamespaces(nd->getNamespaces(),FALSE,addClasses,addConcepts,visitedClasses);
5415 }
5416 if (addClasses)
5417 {
5418 m_children->addClasses(nd->getClasses(),FALSE,visitedClasses);
5419 }
5420 if (addConcepts)
5421 {
5422 m_children->addConcepts(nd->getConcepts(),FALSE,visitedClasses);
5423 }
5424 }
5425 const GroupDef *gd = toGroupDef(m_def);
5426 if (gd)
5427 {
5428 m_children->addConcepts(gd->getConcepts(),false,visitedClasses);
5429 }
5430 }
5431 void addDirFiles(ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5432 {
5433 const DirDef *dd = toDirDef(m_def);
5434 if (dd)
5435 {
5436 m_children->addDirs(dd->subDirs(),visitedClasses);
5437 m_children->addFiles(dd->getFiles(),visitedClasses);
5438 }
5439 const GroupDef *gd = toGroupDef(m_def);
5440 if (gd)
5441 {
5442 m_children->addDirs(gd->getDirs(),visitedClasses);
5443 }
5444 }
5445 void addPages(ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5446 {
5447 const PageDef *pd = toPageDef(m_def);
5448 if (pd && !pd->getSubPages().empty())
5449 {
5450 m_children->addPages(pd->getSubPages(),FALSE,visitedClasses);
5451 }
5452 const GroupDef *gd = toGroupDef(m_def);
5453 if (gd)
5454 {
5455 m_children->addPages(gd->getPages(),FALSE,visitedClasses);
5456 }
5457 }
5458 void addModules(ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5459 {
5460 const GroupDef *gd = toGroupDef(m_def);
5461 if (gd && !gd->getSubGroups().empty())
5462 {
5463 m_children->addModules(gd->getSubGroups(),visitedClasses);
5464 }
5465 }
5466 void addMembers(ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5467 {
5468 if (m_type!=ContextTreeType::Module && m_def->partOfGroups().empty()) // show outside of group
5469 {
5470 if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeNamespace)
5471 {
5472 // add namespace members
5473 for (const auto &lde : LayoutDocManager::instance().docEntries(LayoutDocManager::Namespace))
5474 {
5475 if (lde->kind()==LayoutDocEntry::MemberDef)
5476 {
5477 const LayoutDocEntryMemberDef *lmd = dynamic_cast<const LayoutDocEntryMemberDef*>(lde.get());
5478 if (lmd)
5479 {
5480 const MemberList *ml = toNamespaceDef(m_def)->getMemberList(lmd->type);
5481 if (ml)
5482 {
5483 m_members->addMembers(*ml,visitedClasses);
5484 }
5485 }
5486 }
5487 }
5488 }
5489 else if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeClass)
5490 {
5491 // add class members
5492 for (const auto &lde : LayoutDocManager::instance().docEntries(LayoutDocManager::Class))
5493 {
5494 if (lde->kind()==LayoutDocEntry::MemberDef)
5495 {
5496 const LayoutDocEntryMemberDef *lmd = dynamic_cast<const LayoutDocEntryMemberDef*>(lde.get());
5497 if (lmd)
5498 {
5499 const MemberList *ml = toClassDef(m_def)->getMemberList(lmd->type);
5500 if (ml)
5501 {
5502 m_members->addMembers(*ml,visitedClasses);
5503 }
5504 }
5505 }
5506 }
5507 }
5508 else if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeFile)
5509 {
5510 // add class members
5511 for (const auto &lde : LayoutDocManager::instance().docEntries(LayoutDocManager::File))
5512 {
5513 if (lde->kind()==LayoutDocEntry::MemberDef)
5514 {
5515 const LayoutDocEntryMemberDef *lmd = dynamic_cast<const LayoutDocEntryMemberDef*>(lde.get());
5516 if (lmd)
5517 {
5518 const MemberList *ml = toFileDef(m_def)->getMemberList(lmd->type);
5519 if (ml)
5520 {
5521 m_members->addMembers(*ml,visitedClasses);
5522 }
5523 }
5524 }
5525 }
5526 }
5527 }
5528 else if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeGroup && m_type==ContextTreeType::Module) // show as part of group
5529 {
5530 // add class members
5531 for (const auto &lde : LayoutDocManager::instance().docEntries(LayoutDocManager::Group))
5532 {
5533 if (lde->kind()==LayoutDocEntry::MemberDef)
5534 {
5535 const LayoutDocEntryMemberDef *lmd = dynamic_cast<const LayoutDocEntryMemberDef*>(lde.get());
5536 if (lmd)
5537 {
5538 const MemberList *ml = toGroupDef(m_def)->getMemberList(lmd->type);
5539 if (ml)
5540 {
5541 m_members->addMembers(*ml,visitedClasses);
5542 }
5543 }
5544 }
5545 }
5546 }
5547 if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeMember)
5548 {
5549 const MemberDef *md = toMemberDef(m_def);
5550 if (md->isEnumerate() && md->isStrong())
5551 {
5552 m_members->addMembers(md->enumFieldList(),visitedClasses);
5553 }
5554 }
5555 }
5556 private:
5557 TemplateVariant createClass() const
5558 {
5559 return m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeClass ?
5560 TemplateVariant(ClassContext::alloc(toClassDef(m_def))) :
5561 TemplateVariant(false);
5562 }
5563 TemplateVariant createNamespace() const
5564 {
5565 return m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeNamespace ?
5566 TemplateVariant(NamespaceContext::alloc(toNamespaceDef(m_def))) :
5567 TemplateVariant(false);
5568 }
5569 TemplateVariant createDir() const
5570 {
5571 return m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeDir ?
5572 TemplateVariant(DirContext::alloc(toDirDef(m_def))) :
5573 TemplateVariant(false);
5574 }
5575 TemplateVariant createFile() const
5576 {
5577 return m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeFile ?
5578 TemplateVariant(FileContext::alloc(toFileDef(m_def))) :
5579 TemplateVariant(false);
5580 }
5581 TemplateVariant createPage() const
5582 {
5583 return m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypePage ?
5584 TemplateVariant(PageContext::alloc(toPageDef(m_def),FALSE,FALSE)) :
5585 TemplateVariant(false);
5586 }
5587 TemplateVariant createModule() const
5588 {
5589 return m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeGroup ?
5590 TemplateVariant(ModuleContext::alloc(toGroupDef(m_def))) :
5591 TemplateVariant(false);
5592 }
5593 TemplateVariant createMember() const
5594 {
5595 return m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeMember ?
5596 TemplateVariant(MemberContext::alloc(toMemberDef(m_def))) :
5597 TemplateVariant(false);
5598 }
5599 TemplateVariant createBrief() const
5600 {
5601 return m_def->hasBriefDescription() ?
5602 TemplateVariant(parseDoc(m_def,m_def->briefFile(),m_def->briefLine(),
5603 "",m_def->briefDescription(),TRUE)) :
5604 TemplateVariant("");
5605 }
5606
5607 const NestingNodeContext *m_parent;
5608 ContextTreeType m_type;
5609 const Definition *m_def;
5610 std::shared_ptr<NestingContext> m_children;
5611 std::shared_ptr<NestingContext> m_members;
5612 int m_level;
5613 int m_index;
5614 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createClass> m_class;
5615 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createNamespace> m_namespace;
5616 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDir> m_dir;
5617 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createFile> m_file;
5618 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createPage> m_page;
5619 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createModule> m_module;
5620 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createMember> m_member;
5621 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createBrief> m_brief;
5622 static const PropertyMap<NestingNodeContext::Private> s_inst;
5623};
5624
5625//%% struct NestingNode: node is a nesting relation tree

5629 { "is_leaf_node",&Private::isLeafNode },
5630 //%% Nesting children: list of nested classes/namespaces

5641 { "dir",&Private::getDir },

5643 { "page",&Private::getPage },
5644 //%% [optional] Module module: module info (if this node represents a module)
5645 { "module",&Private::getModule },

5647 { "member",&Private::getMember },

5650 //%% string level

5659 { "anchor",&Private::anchor },

5696//------------------------------------------------------------------------
5697
5698//%% list Nesting[NestingNode]: namespace and class nesting relations
5699class NestingContext::Private : public GenericNodeListContext
5700{
5701 public:
5702 Private(const NestingNodeContext *parent,ContextTreeType type,int level)
5703 : m_parent(parent), m_type(type), m_level(level) {}
5704
5705 void addNamespace(const NamespaceDef *nd,bool rootOnly,bool addClasses,bool addConcepts,
5706 ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5707 {
5708 if (!nd->isAnonymous() &&
5709 (!rootOnly || nd->getOuterScope()==Doxygen::globalScope))
5710 {
5711 bool hasChildren = namespaceHasNestedNamespace(nd) ||
5712 (addClasses && namespaceHasNestedClass(nd,false,ClassDef::Class)) ||
5713 (addConcepts && namespaceHasNestedConcept(nd)) ||
5714 (m_type==ContextTreeType::Namespace && nd->countVisibleMembers());
5715 bool isLinkable = nd->isLinkableInProject();
5716 if (isLinkable && hasChildren)
5717 {
5718 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,nd,m_index,m_level,
5719 addClasses,addConcepts,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5720 m_index++;
5721 }
5722 }
5723 }
5724 void addNamespaces(const NamespaceLinkedMap &nsLinkedMap,bool rootOnly,bool addClasses,bool addConcepts,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5725 {
5726 for (const auto &nd : nsLinkedMap)
5727 {
5728 addNamespace(nd.get(),rootOnly,addClasses,addConcepts,visitedClasses);
5729 }
5730 }
5731 void addNamespaces(const NamespaceLinkedRefMap &nsLinkedMap,bool rootOnly,bool addClasses,bool addConcepts,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5732 {
5733 for (const auto &nd : nsLinkedMap)
5734 {
5735 addNamespace(nd,rootOnly,addClasses,addConcepts,visitedClasses);
5736 }
5737 }
5738 void addClass(const ClassDef *cd,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5739 {
5740 if (cd->getLanguage()==SrcLangExt_VHDL)
5741 {
5742 if (VhdlDocGen::convert(cd->protection())==VhdlDocGen::PACKAGECLASS ||
5743 VhdlDocGen::convert(cd->protection())==VhdlDocGen::PACKBODYCLASS
5744 )// no architecture
5745 {
5746 return;
5747 }
5748 }
5749 if (!rootOnly ||
5750 cd->getOuterScope()==0 ||
5751 cd->getOuterScope()==Doxygen::globalScope
5752 )
5753 {
5754 if (classVisibleInIndex(cd) && cd->templateMaster()==0)
5755 {
5756 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,cd,m_index,m_level,
5757 TRUE,FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5758 m_index++;
5759 }
5760 }
5761 }
5762 void addConcept(const ConceptDef *cd,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5763 {
5764 if (!rootOnly || cd->getOuterScope()==0 || cd->getOuterScope()==Doxygen::globalScope)
5765 {
5766 if (cd->isLinkable())
5767 {
5768 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,cd,m_index,m_level,
5769 FALSE,TRUE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5770 m_index++;
5771 }
5772 }
5773 }
5774 void addClasses(const ClassLinkedRefMap &clLinkedMap,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5775 {
5776 for (const auto &cd : clLinkedMap)
5777 {
5778 addClass(cd,rootOnly,visitedClasses);
5779 }
5780 }
5781 void addClasses(const ClassLinkedMap &clLinkedMap,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5782 {
5783 for (const auto &cd : clLinkedMap)
5784 {
5785 addClass(cd.get(),rootOnly,visitedClasses);
5786 }
5787 }
5788 void addConcepts(const ConceptLinkedRefMap &cpLinkedMap,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5789 {
5790 for (const auto &cd : cpLinkedMap)
5791 {
5792 addConcept(cd,rootOnly,visitedClasses);
5793 }
5794 }
5795 void addConcepts(const ConceptLinkedMap &cpLinkedMap,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5796 {
5797 for (const auto &cd : cpLinkedMap)
5798 {
5799 addConcept(cd.get(),rootOnly,visitedClasses);
5800 }
5801 }
5802 void addDirs(const DirLinkedMap &dirLinkedMap,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5803 {
5804 for (const auto &dd : dirLinkedMap)
5805 {
5806 if (dd->getOuterScope()==Doxygen::globalScope)
5807 {
5808 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,dd.get(),m_index,m_level,
5809 FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5810 m_index++;
5811 }
5812 }
5813 }
5814 void addDirs(const DirList &dirList,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5815 {
5816 for(const auto dd : dirList)
5817 {
5818 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,dd,m_index,m_level,
5819 FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5820 m_index++;
5821 }
5822 }
5823 void addFiles(const FileNameLinkedMap &fnList,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5824 {
5825 for (const FileNameLinkedMap::Ptr &fn : fnList)
5826 {
5827 for (const auto &fd : *fn)
5828 {
5829 if (fd->getDirDef()==0) // top level file
5830 {
5831 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,fd.get(),m_index,m_level,
5832 FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5833 m_index++;
5834 }
5835 }
5836 }
5837 }
5838 void addFiles(const FileList &fList,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5839 {
5840 for (const auto &fd : fList)
5841 {
5842 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,fd,m_index,m_level,
5843 FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5844 m_index++;
5845 }
5846 }
5847 void addPage(const PageDef *pd,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5848 {
5849 if (!rootOnly ||
5850 pd->getOuterScope()==0 ||
5851 pd->getOuterScope()->definitionType()!=Definition::TypePage)
5852 {
5853 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,pd,m_index,m_level,
5854 FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5855 m_index++;
5856 }
5857 }
5858 void addPages(const PageLinkedMap &pages,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5859 {
5860 for (const auto &pd : pages)
5861 {
5862 addPage(pd.get(),rootOnly,visitedClasses);
5863 }
5864 }
5865 void addPages(const PageLinkedRefMap &pages,bool rootOnly,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5866 {
5867 for (const auto &pd : pages)
5868 {
5869 addPage(pd,rootOnly,visitedClasses);
5870 }
5871 }
5872 void addModules(const GroupLinkedMap &groups,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5873 {
5874 for (const auto &gd : groups)
5875 {
5876 bool externalGroups = Config_getBool(EXTERNAL_GROUPS);
5877 if (!gd->isASubGroup() && gd->isVisible() &&
5878 (!gd->isReference() || externalGroups)
5879 )
5880 {
5881 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,gd.get(),m_index,m_level,
5882 FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5883 m_index++;
5884 }
5885 }
5886 }
5887 void addModules(const GroupList &groups,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5888 {
5889 for (const auto &gd : groups)
5890 {
5891 if (gd->isVisible())
5892 {
5893 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,gd,m_index,m_level,
5894 FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5895 m_index++;
5896 }
5897 }
5898 }
5899 void addDerivedClasses(const BaseClassList &bcl,bool hideSuper,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5900 {
5901 for (const auto &bcd : bcl)
5902 {
5903 const ClassDef *cd=bcd.classDef;
5904 if (cd->getLanguage()==SrcLangExt_VHDL && VhdlDocGen::convert(cd->protection())!=VhdlDocGen::ENTITYCLASS)
5905 {
5906 continue;
5907 }
5908
5909 bool b;
5910 if (cd->getLanguage()==SrcLangExt_VHDL)
5911 {
5912 b=classHasVisibleRoot(cd->subClasses());
5913 }
5914 else
5915 {
5916 b=classHasVisibleRoot(cd->baseClasses());
5917 }
5918
5919 if (cd->isVisibleInHierarchy() && b)
5920 {
5921 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,cd,m_index,m_level,
5922 TRUE,FALSE,TRUE,hideSuper,visitedClasses));
5923 m_index++;
5924 }
5925 }
5926 }
5927 void addClassHierarchy(const ClassLinkedMap &classLinkedMap,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5928 {
5929 for (const auto &cd : classLinkedMap)
5930 {
5931 bool b;
5932 if (cd->getLanguage()==SrcLangExt_VHDL)
5933 {
5934 if (VhdlDocGen::convert(cd->protection())!=VhdlDocGen::ENTITYCLASS)
5935 {
5936 continue;
5937 }
5938 b=!classHasVisibleRoot(cd->subClasses());
5939 }
5940 else
5941 {
5942 b=!classHasVisibleRoot(cd->baseClasses());
5943 }
5944 if (b)
5945 {
5946 if (cd->isVisibleInHierarchy()) // should it be visible
5947 {
5948 // new root level class
5949 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,cd.get(),m_index,m_level,
5950 TRUE,FALSE,TRUE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5951 m_index++;
5952 }
5953 }
5954 }
5955 }
5956 void addMembers(const MemberVector &mv,ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
5957 {
5958 for (const auto &md : mv)
5959 {
5960 if (md->visibleInIndex())
5961 {
5962 append(NestingNodeContext::alloc(m_parent,m_type,md,m_index,m_level+1,
5963 TRUE,FALSE,TRUE,FALSE,visitedClasses));
5964 m_index++;
5965 }
5966 }
5967 }
5968
5969 private:
5970 const NestingNodeContext *m_parent;
5971 ContextTreeType m_type;
5972 int m_level;
5973 int m_index = 0;
5974};
5975
5976NestingContext::NestingContext(const NestingNodeContext *parent,ContextTreeType type,int level) : p(std::make_unique<Private>(parent,type,level))
5977{
5978}

5981{
5982}

6092 {

6094 auto ctx = std::dynamic_pointer_cast<NestingContext>(m_classTree);
6095 ClassDefSet visitedClasses;
6096 ctx->addNamespaces(*Doxygen::namespaceLinkedMap,TRUE,TRUE,FALSE,visitedClasses);
6097 ctx->addClasses(*Doxygen::classLinkedMap,TRUE,visitedClasses);
6098 }

6100 // TemplateStructIntf methods

6112 TemplateVariant preferredDepth() const { return m_preferredDepth.get(this); }

6114 {

6130 CachedItem<int, Private, &Private::createPreferredDepth> m_preferredDepth;
6131 static const PropertyMap<ClassTreeContext::Private> s_inst;
6132};

6338//%% list FileList[File] : list of files
6339class FileListContext::Private : public GenericNodeListContext
6340{
6341 public:
6342 void addFiles(const FileNameLinkedMap &fnMap)
6343 {
6344 // TODO: if FULL_PATH_NAMES is enabled, the ordering should be dir+file
6345 for (const auto &fn : fnMap)
6346 {
6347 for (const auto &fd : *fn)
6348 {
6349 bool doc = fd->isLinkableInProject();
6350 bool src = fd->generateSourceFile();
6351 bool nameOk = !fd->isDocumentationFile();
6352 if (nameOk && (doc || src) && !fd->isReference())
6353 {
6354 append(FileContext::alloc(fd.get()));
6355 }
6356 }
6357 }
6358 }
6359};
6360
6361FileListContext::FileListContext() : p(std::make_unique<Private>())
6362{
6363 if (Doxygen::inputNameLinkedMap) p->addFiles(*Doxygen::inputNameLinkedMap);
6364}

6366FileListContext::~FileListContext()
6367{
6368}

6377{
6378 return p->at(index);

6763class ConceptTreeContext::Private
6764{
6765 public:
6766 Private()
6767 {
6768 m_conceptTree = NestingContext::alloc(0,ContextTreeType::Concept,0);
6769 auto ctx = std::dynamic_pointer_cast<NestingContext>(m_conceptTree);
6770 ClassDefSet visitedClasses;
6771 // Add concepts
6772 ctx->addNamespaces(*Doxygen::namespaceLinkedMap,TRUE,FALSE,TRUE,visitedClasses);
6773 ctx->addConcepts(*Doxygen::conceptLinkedMap,TRUE,visitedClasses);
6774 }
6775
6776 // TemplateStructIntf methods
6777 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
6778 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
6779
6780 private:
6781 // Property getters
6782 TemplateVariant tree() const { return TemplateVariant(m_conceptTree); }
6783 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return "concepts"; }
6784 TemplateVariant relPath() const { return ""; }
6785 TemplateVariant highlight() const { return "concepts"; }
6786 TemplateVariant subhighlight() const { return ""; }
6787 TemplateVariant maxDepth() const { return m_maxDepth.get(this); }
6788 TemplateVariant preferredDepth() const { return m_preferredDepth.get(this); }
6789 TemplateVariant title() const { return theTranslator->trConcept(true,false); }
6790
6791 private:
6792 int createMaxDepth() const
6793 {
6794 return computeMaxDepth(m_conceptTree);
6795 }
6796 int createPreferredDepth() const
6797 {
6798 return computePreferredDepth(m_conceptTree,m_maxDepth.get(this));
6799 }
6800 TemplateListIntfPtr m_conceptTree;
6801 CachedItem<int, Private, &Private::createMaxDepth> m_maxDepth;
6802 CachedItem<int, Private, &Private::createPreferredDepth> m_preferredDepth;
6803 static const PropertyMap<ConceptTreeContext::Private> s_inst;
6804};

6995
6996class NavPathElemContext::Private
6997{
6998 public:
6999 Private(const Definition *def) : m_def(def) {}
7000
7001 // TemplateStructIntf methods
7002 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
7003 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
7004
7005 private:
7006 // Property getters
7007 TemplateVariant isLinkable() const { return m_def->isLinkable(); }
7008 TemplateVariant anchor() const { return m_def->anchor(); }
7009 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return m_def->getOutputFileBase(); }
7010 TemplateVariant isReference() const { return m_def->isReference(); }
7011 TemplateVariant externalReference() const { return m_def->externalReference(relPathAsString()); }
7012 TemplateVariant text() const
7013 {
7014 Definition::DefType type = m_def->definitionType();
7015 QCString text = m_def->localName();
7016 if (type==Definition::TypeGroup)
7017 {
7018 text = (toGroupDef(m_def))->groupTitle();
7019 }
7020 else if (type==Definition::TypePage && ((toPageDef(m_def))->hasTitle()))
7021 {
7022 text = (toPageDef(m_def))->title();
7023 }
7024 else if (type==Definition::TypeClass)
7025 {
7026 if (text.endsWith("-p"))
7027 {
7028 text = text.left(text.length()-2);
7029 }
7030 }
7031 return text;
7032 }
7033 QCString relPathAsString() const
7034 {
7035 bool createSubdirs = Config_getBool(CREATE_SUBDIRS);
7036 return createSubdirs ? QCString("../../") : QCString("");
7037 }
7038 private:
7039 const Definition *m_def;
7040 static const PropertyMap<NavPathElemContext::Private> s_inst;
7041};
7042
7043//%% struct NavPathElem: list of examples page
7044//%% {
7045const PropertyMap<NavPathElemContext::Private> NavPathElemContext::Private::s_inst {
7046 { "isLinkable", &Private::isLinkable },
7047 { "fileName", &Private::fileName },
7048 { "anchor", &Private::anchor },
7049 { "text", &Private::text },
7050 { "isReference", &Private::isReference },
7051 { "externalReference",&Private::externalReference }
7052};
7053//%% }
7054
7055
7056NavPathElemContext::NavPathElemContext(const Definition *def) : p(std::make_unique<Private>(def))
7057{
7058}
7059
7060NavPathElemContext::~NavPathElemContext()
7061{
7062}

7065{
7066 return p->get(name);

7069StringVector NavPathElemContext::fields() const
7070{

7076class GlobalsIndexContext::Private
7077{
7078 public:
7079 // TemplateStructIntf methods
7080 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
7081 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
7082
7083 private:
7084 // Property getters
7085 TemplateVariant all() const { return m_all.get(this); }
7086 TemplateVariant functions() const { return m_functions.get(this); }
7087 TemplateVariant variables() const { return m_variables.get(this); }
7088 TemplateVariant typedefs() const { return m_typedefs.get(this); }
7089 TemplateVariant enums() const { return m_enums.get(this); }
7090 TemplateVariant enumValues() const { return m_enumValues.get(this); }
7091 TemplateVariant macros() const { return m_macros.get(this); }
7092 TemplateVariant properties() const { return FALSE; }
7093 TemplateVariant events() const { return FALSE; }
7094 TemplateVariant related() const { return FALSE; }
7095 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return "globals"; }
7096 TemplateVariant relPath() const { return ""; }
7097 TemplateVariant highlight() const { return "files"; }
7098 TemplateVariant subhighlight() const { return "filemembers"; }
7099 TemplateVariant title() const { return theTranslator->trFileMembers(); }
7100
7101 private:
7102 using MemberFilter = bool (MemberDef::*)() const;
7103 TemplateVariant createMembersFiltered(MemberFilter filter) const
7104 {
7105 TemplateVariantList list;
7106 for (const auto &mn : *Doxygen::functionNameLinkedMap)
7107 {
7108 for (const auto &md : *mn)
7109 {
7110 const FileDef *fd=md->getFileDef();
7111 if (fd && fd->isLinkableInProject() &&
7112 !md->name().isEmpty() && !md->getNamespaceDef() && md->isLinkableInProject())
7113 {
7114 if (filter==0 || (md.get()->*filter)())
7115 {
7116 list.push_back(MemberContext::alloc(md.get()));
7117 }
7118 }
7119 }
7120 }
7121 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
7122 }
7123 TemplateVariant createAll() const { return createMembersFiltered(0); }
7124 TemplateVariant createFunctions() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isFunction); }
7125 TemplateVariant createVariables() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isVariable); }
7126 TemplateVariant createTypedefs() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isTypedef); }
7127 TemplateVariant createEnums() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isEnumerate); }
7128 TemplateVariant createEnumValues() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isEnumValue); }
7129 TemplateVariant createMacros() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isDefine); }
7130
7131 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createAll> m_all;
7132 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createFunctions> m_functions;
7133 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createVariables> m_variables;
7134 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createTypedefs> m_typedefs;
7135 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createEnums> m_enums;
7136 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createEnumValues> m_enumValues;
7137 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createMacros> m_macros;
7138 static const PropertyMap<GlobalsIndexContext::Private> s_inst;
7139};

7183class ClassMembersIndexContext::Private
7184{
7185 public:
7186 // TemplateStructIntf methods
7187 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
7188 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
7189
7190 private:
7191 // Property getters
7192 TemplateVariant all() const { return m_all.get(this); }
7193 TemplateVariant functions() const { return m_functions.get(this); }
7194 TemplateVariant variables() const { return m_variables.get(this); }
7195 TemplateVariant typedefs() const { return m_typedefs.get(this); }
7196 TemplateVariant enums() const { return m_enums.get(this); }
7197 TemplateVariant enumValues() const { return m_enumValues.get(this); }
7198 TemplateVariant macros() const { return FALSE; }
7199 TemplateVariant properties() const { return m_properties.get(this); }
7200 TemplateVariant events() const { return m_events.get(this); }
7201 TemplateVariant related() const { return m_related.get(this); }
7202 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return "functions"; }
7203 TemplateVariant relPath() const { return ""; }
7204 TemplateVariant highlight() const { return "classes"; }
7205 TemplateVariant subhighlight() const { return "classmembers"; }
7206 TemplateVariant title() const { return theTranslator->trCompoundMembers(); }
7207
7208 private:
7209 using MemberFilter = bool (MemberDef::*)() const;
7210 TemplateVariant createMembersFiltered(MemberFilter filter) const
7211 {
7212 TemplateVariantList list;
7213 for (const auto &mn : *Doxygen::memberNameLinkedMap)
7214 {
7215 for (const auto &md : *mn)
7216 {
7217 const ClassDef *cd = md->getClassDef();
7218 if (cd && cd->isLinkableInProject() && cd->templateMaster()==0 &&
7219 md->isLinkableInProject() && !md->name().isEmpty())
7220 {
7221 if (filter==0 || (md.get()->*filter)())
7222 {
7223 list.push_back(MemberContext::alloc(md.get()));
7224 }
7225 }
7226 }
7227 }
7228 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
7229 }
7230 TemplateVariant createAll() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isNotFriend); }
7231 TemplateVariant createFunctions() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isFunctionOrSignalSlot); }
7232 TemplateVariant createVariables() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isVariable); }
7233 TemplateVariant createTypedefs() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isTypedef); }
7234 TemplateVariant createEnums() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isEnumerate); }
7235 TemplateVariant createEnumValues() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isEnumValue); }
7236 TemplateVariant createProperties() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isProperty); }
7237 TemplateVariant createEvents() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isEvent); }
7238 TemplateVariant createRelated() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isRelated); }
7239
7240 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createAll> m_all;
7241 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createFunctions> m_functions;
7242 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createVariables> m_variables;
7243 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createTypedefs> m_typedefs;
7244 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createEnums> m_enums;
7245 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createEnumValues> m_enumValues;
7246 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createProperties> m_properties;
7247 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createEvents> m_events;
7248 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createRelated> m_related;
7249 static const PropertyMap<ClassMembersIndexContext::Private> s_inst;
7250};

7308 TemplateVariant enumValues() const { return m_enumValues.get(this); }
7309 TemplateVariant macros() const { return FALSE; }
7310 TemplateVariant properties() const { return FALSE; }
7311 TemplateVariant events() const { return FALSE; }
7312 TemplateVariant related() const { return FALSE; }
7313 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return "namespacemembers"; }
7314 TemplateVariant relPath() const { return ""; }
7315 TemplateVariant highlight() const { return "namespaces"; }
7316 TemplateVariant subhighlight() const { return "namespacemembers"; }
7317 TemplateVariant title() const { return theTranslator->trNamespaceMembers(); }
7318
7319 private:
7320 using MemberFilter = bool (MemberDef::*)() const;
7321 TemplateVariant createMembersFiltered(MemberFilter filter) const
7322 {
7323 TemplateVariantList list;
7324 for (const auto &mn : *Doxygen::functionNameLinkedMap)
7325 {
7326 for (const auto &md : *mn)
7327 {
7328 const NamespaceDef *nd=md->getNamespaceDef();
7329 if (nd && nd->isLinkableInProject() &&
7330 !md->name().isEmpty() && md->isLinkableInProject())
7331 {
7332 if (filter==0 || (md.get()->*filter)())
7333 {
7334 list.push_back(MemberContext::alloc(md.get()));
7335 }
7336 }
7337 }
7338 }
7339 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc(list);
7340 }
7341
7342 TemplateVariant createAll() const { return createMembersFiltered(0); }
7343 TemplateVariant createFunctions() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isFunction); }
7344 TemplateVariant createVariables() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isVariable); }
7345 TemplateVariant createTypedefs() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isTypedef); }
7346 TemplateVariant createEnums() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isEnumerate); }
7347 TemplateVariant createEnumValues() const { return createMembersFiltered(&MemberDef::isEnumValue); }
7348
7349 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createAll> m_all;
7350 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createFunctions> m_functions;
7351 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createVariables> m_variables;
7352 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createTypedefs> m_typedefs;
7353 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createEnums> m_enums;
7354 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createEnumValues> m_enumValues;
7355 static const PropertyMap<NamespaceMembersIndexContext::Private> s_inst;
7356};
7357
7358//%% struct NamespaceMembersIndex: list of examples page
7359//%% {

7361 { "all", &Private::all },
7362 { "functions", &Private::functions },
7363 { "variables", &Private::variables },
7364 { "typedefs", &Private::typedefs },
7365 { "enums", &Private::enums },
7366 { "enumValues", &Private::enumValues },
7367 { "macros", &Private::macros },
7368 { "properties", &Private::properties },

7370 { "related", &Private::related },

7416 {
7417 TextStream t;
7418 bool haveDot = Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT);
7419 bool graphicalHierarchy = Config_getBool(GRAPHICAL_HIERARCHY);
7420 if (haveDot && graphicalHierarchy)
7421 {
7422 m_hierarchy->createGraph(m_node,t,
7423 /*GOF_BITMAP,
7424 EOF_Html,*/
7425 g_globals.outputDir,
7426 g_globals.outputDir+Portable::pathSeparator()+"inherits"+Doxygen::htmlFileExtension,
7427 m_id);
7428 }
7429 return TemplateVariant(t.str().c_str(),TRUE);
7430 }

7524 {

7526 }
7527};
7528
7529InheritanceListContext::InheritanceListContext(const BaseClassList &list, bool baseClasses) : p(std::make_unique<Private>())
7530{
7531 for (const auto &bcd : list)
7532 {
7533 const ClassDef *cd=bcd.classDef;
7534 QCString name;
7535 if (baseClasses)
7536 {
7537 name = insertTemplateSpecifierInScope(
7538 cd->displayName(),bcd.templSpecifiers);
7539 }
7540 else
7541 {
7542 name = cd->displayName();
7543 }
7544 //printf("InheritanceListContext: adding %s baseClass=%d\n",qPrint(name),baseClasses);
7545 p->addClass(cd,name);
7546 }
7547}

7550{

7586{

7588 {

7592 if ((md->isBriefSectionVisible() && !details) ||
7593 (md->hasDetailedDescription() && details)
7594 )

7596 p->addMember(md);
7597 }
7598 }

7632class MemberInfoContext::Private
7633{
7634 public:
7635 Private(const MemberInfo *mi) : m_memberInfo(mi) {}
7636
7637 // TemplateStructIntf methods

7640
7641 private:
7642 // Property getters
7643 TemplateVariant protection() const
7644 {
7645 switch (m_memberInfo->prot())
7646 {
7647 case Protection::Public: return "public";
7648 case Protection::Protected: return "protected";
7649 case Protection::Private: return "private";
7650 case Protection::Package: return "package";
7651 }
7652 return "";
7653 }
7654 TemplateVariant virtualness() const
7655 {
7656 switch (m_memberInfo->virt())
7657 {
7658 case Specifier::Normal: return "normal";
7659 case Specifier::Virtual: return "virtual";
7660 case Specifier::Pure: return "pure";
7661 }
7662 return "";
7663 }
7664 TemplateVariant ambiguityScope() const
7665 {
7666 return m_memberInfo->ambiguityResolutionScope();
7667 }
7668 TemplateVariant member() const
7669 {
7670 return m_member.get(this);
7671 }
7672
7673 private:
7674 TemplateVariant createMember() const
7675 {
7676 return m_memberInfo->memberDef() ?
7677 TemplateVariant(MemberContext::alloc(m_memberInfo->memberDef())) :
7678 TemplateVariant(false);
7679 }
7680 const MemberInfo *m_memberInfo;
7681 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createMember> m_member;
7682 static const PropertyMap<MemberInfoContext::Private> s_inst;
7683};

7719//%% list AllMembersList[MemberList] : list of inherited classes
7720class AllMembersListContext::Private : public GenericNodeListContext
7721{
7722 public:
7723 Private(const MemberNameInfoLinkedMap &ml)
7724 {
7725 bool hideUndocMembers = Config_getBool(HIDE_UNDOC_MEMBERS);
7726 for (auto &mni : ml)
7727 {
7728 for (auto &mi : *mni)
7729 {
7730 const MemberDef *md=mi->memberDef();
7731 const ClassDef *cd=md->getClassDef();
7732 if (cd && !md->isAnonymous())
7733 {
7734 if ((cd->isLinkable() && md->isLinkable()) ||
7735 (!cd->isArtificial() && !hideUndocMembers &&
7736 (protectionLevelVisible(md->protection()) || md->isFriend())
7737 )
7738 )
7739 {
7740 append(MemberInfoContext::alloc(mi.get()));
7741 }
7742 }
7743 }
7744 }
7745 }
7746};
7747
7748AllMembersListContext::AllMembersListContext(const MemberNameInfoLinkedMap &ml) : p(std::make_unique<Private>(ml))
7749{
7750}
7751
7752AllMembersListContext::~AllMembersListContext()
7753{
7754}

7757size_t AllMembersListContext::count() const
7758{
7759 return p->count();
7760}

7763{
7764 return p->at(index);
7765}

7768{

7908class MemberListInfoContext::Private
7909{
7910 public:
7911 Private(const Definition *def,const QCString &relPath,const MemberList *ml,const QCString &title,const QCString &subtitle)
7912 : m_def(def), m_memberList(ml), m_relPath(relPath), m_title(title), m_subtitle(subtitle) {}
7913
7914 // TemplateStructIntf methods
7915 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
7916 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
7917
7918 private:
7919 // Property getters
7920 TemplateVariant members() const { return m_memberListCtx.get(this); }
7921 TemplateVariant title() const { return m_title; }
7922 TemplateVariant subtitle() const { return m_subtitle; }
7923 TemplateVariant anchor() const { return MemberList::listTypeAsString(m_memberList->listType()); }
7924 TemplateVariant memberGroups() const { return m_memberGroups.get(this); }
7925 TemplateVariant inherited() const { return m_inherited.get(this); }
7926
7927 private:
7928

7930 {
7931 return MemberListContext::alloc(m_memberList);
7932 }
7933 TemplateVariant createMemberGroups() const
7934 {
7935 return MemberGroupListContext::alloc(m_def,m_relPath,m_memberList->getMemberGroupList());
7936 }
7937 TemplateVariant createInherited() const
7938 {
7939 if ((m_memberList->listType()&MemberListType_detailedLists)==0 &&
7940 m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeClass)
7941 {
7942 TemplateListIntfPtr list = InheritedMemberInfoListContext::alloc();
7943 auto ctx = std::dynamic_pointer_cast<InheritedMemberInfoListContext>(list);
7944 ctx->addMemberList(toClassDef(m_def),m_memberList->listType(),m_title,FALSE);
7945 return list;
7946 }
7947 else
7948 {
7949 return TemplateVariant(false);
7950 }
7951 }
7952 const Definition *m_def;
7953 const MemberList *m_memberList;
7954 QCString m_relPath;
7955 QCString m_title;
7956 QCString m_subtitle;
7957 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createMemberList> m_memberListCtx;
7958 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createMemberGroups> m_memberGroups;
7959 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createInherited> m_inherited;
7960 static const PropertyMap<MemberListInfoContext::Private> s_inst;
7961};

7997class InheritedMemberInfoContext::Private
7998{
7999 public:
8000 Private(const ClassDef *cd,std::unique_ptr<MemberList> &&ml,const QCString &title)
8001 : m_class(cd), m_memberList(std::move(ml)), m_title(title) {}
8002
8003 // TemplateStructIntf methods
8004 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
8005 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
8006
8007 private:
8008 // Property getters
8009 TemplateVariant getClass() const { return m_classCtx.get(this); }
8010 TemplateVariant title() const { return m_title; }
8011 TemplateVariant members() const { return m_memberListCtx.get(this); }
8012 TemplateVariant inheritedFrom() const { return m_inheritedFrom.get(this); }
8013 TemplateVariant id() const
8014 {
8015 return substitute(MemberList::listTypeAsString(m_memberList->listType()),"-","_")+"_"+
8016 stripPath(m_class->getOutputFileBase());
8017 }
8018
8019 private:
8020 TemplateVariant createClass() const
8021 {
8022 return ClassContext::alloc(m_class);
8023 }
8024 TemplateVariant createMemberList() const
8025 {
8026 return MemberListContext::alloc(m_memberList.get());
8027 }
8028 TemplateVariant createInheritedFrom() const
8029 {
8030 return TemplateImmutableList::alloc({ TemplateVariant(title()), TemplateVariant(getClass()) });
8031 }
8032
8033 const ClassDef * m_class;
8034 std::unique_ptr<const MemberList> m_memberList;
8035 QCString m_title;
8036 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createClass> m_classCtx;
8037 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createMemberList> m_memberListCtx;
8038 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createInheritedFrom> m_inheritedFrom;
8039 static const PropertyMap<InheritedMemberInfoContext::Private> s_inst;
8040};

8042//%% struct InheritedMemberInfo: inherited member information
8043//%% {
8044const PropertyMap<InheritedMemberInfoContext::Private> InheritedMemberInfoContext::Private::s_inst {
8045 { "class", &Private::getClass },
8046 { "title", &Private::title },
8047 { "members", &Private::members },
8048 { "id", &Private::id },
8049 { "inheritedFrom", &Private::inheritedFrom }
8050};
8051//%% }

8054 : p(std::make_unique<Private>(cd,std::move(ml),title))
8055{
8056}

8072//------------------------------------------------------------------------
8073
8074//%% list InheritedMemberList[InheritedMemberInfo] : list of inherited classes
8075class InheritedMemberInfoListContext::Private : public GenericNodeListContext
8076{
8077 public:
8078 void addMemberList(const ClassDef *inheritedFrom,const MemberList &ml,MemberList *combinedList)
8079 {
8080 for (const auto &md : ml)
8081 {
8082 if (md->isBriefSectionVisible() && !md->isReimplementedBy(inheritedFrom))
8083 {
8084 combinedList->push_back(md);
8085 }
8086 }
8087 }
8088 void addMemberListIncludingGrouped(const ClassDef *inheritedFrom,const MemberList *ml,MemberList *combinedList)
8089 {
8090 if (ml)
8091 {
8092 addMemberList(inheritedFrom,*ml,combinedList);
8093 for (const auto *mg : ml->getMemberGroupList())
8094 {
8095 addMemberList(inheritedFrom,mg->members(),combinedList);
8096 }
8097 }
8098 }
8099 void addMemberGroupsOfClass(const ClassDef *inheritedFrom,
8100 const ClassDef *cd,MemberListType lt,MemberList *combinedList)
8101 {
8102 // TODO: why this there no addMemberGroupsOfNamespace, addMembersGroupsOfFile,
8103 // addMemberGroupsOfGroup?
8104 for (const auto &mg: cd->getMemberGroups())
8105 {
8106 if (!mg->members().empty() && (!mg->allMembersInSameSection() || !cd->subGrouping())) // group is in its own section
8107 {
8108 for (const auto &md : mg->members())
8109 {
8110 if (lt==md->getSectionList(mg->container())->listType() &&
8111 !md->isReimplementedBy(inheritedFrom) &&
8112 md->isBriefSectionVisible())
8113 {
8114 combinedList->push_back(md);
8115 }
8116 }
8117 }
8118 }
8119 }
8120 void addInheritedMembers(const ClassDef *inheritedFrom,const ClassDef *cd,MemberListType lt,
8121 MemberListType lt1,int lt2,const QCString &title,bool additionalList)
8122 {
8123 int count = cd->countMembersIncludingGrouped(lt1,inheritedFrom,additionalList);
8124 if (lt2!=-1) count += cd->countMembersIncludingGrouped(static_cast<MemberListType>(lt2),inheritedFrom,additionalList);
8125 if (count>0)
8126 {
8127 const MemberList *ml = cd->getMemberList(lt1);
8128 const MemberList *ml2 = lt2!=-1 ? cd->getMemberList(static_cast<MemberListType>(lt2)) : 0;
8129 std::unique_ptr<MemberList> combinedList = std::make_unique<MemberList>(lt,MemberListContainer::Class);
8130 addMemberListIncludingGrouped(inheritedFrom,ml,combinedList.get());
8131 addMemberListIncludingGrouped(inheritedFrom,ml2,combinedList.get());
8132 addMemberGroupsOfClass(inheritedFrom,cd,lt,combinedList.get());
8133 if (lt2!=-1) addMemberGroupsOfClass(inheritedFrom,cd,static_cast<MemberListType>(lt2),combinedList.get());
8134 append(InheritedMemberInfoContext::alloc(cd,std::move(combinedList),title));
8135 }
8136 }
8137 void findInheritedMembers(const ClassDef *inheritedFrom,const ClassDef *cd,MemberListType lt,
8138 int lt2, const QCString &title,bool additionalList,
8139 ClassDefSet &visitedClasses)
8140 {
8141 for (const auto &ibcd : cd->baseClasses())
8142 {
8143 ClassDef *icd=ibcd.classDef;
8144 if (icd->isLinkable())
8145 {
8146 int lt1,lt3;
8147 convertProtectionLevel(lt,ibcd.prot,&lt1,&lt3);
8148 if (lt2==-1 && lt3!=-1)
8149 {
8150 lt2=lt3;
8151 }
8152 if (visitedClasses.find(icd)==visitedClasses.end())
8153 {
8154 visitedClasses.insert(icd); // guard for multiple virtual inheritance
8155 if (lt1!=-1)
8156 {
8157 // add member info for members of cd with list type lt
8158 addInheritedMembers(inheritedFrom,icd,lt,static_cast<MemberListType>(lt1),lt2,title,additionalList);
8159 // recurse down the inheritance tree
8160 findInheritedMembers(inheritedFrom,icd,static_cast<MemberListType>(lt1),lt2,title,additionalList,visitedClasses);
8161 }
8162 }
8163 }
8164 }
8165 }
8166};
8167
8168InheritedMemberInfoListContext::InheritedMemberInfoListContext() : p(std::make_unique<Private>())
8169{
8170}
8171
8172void InheritedMemberInfoListContext::addMemberList(
8173 const ClassDef *cd,MemberListType lt,const QCString &title,bool additionalList)
8174{
8175 ClassDefSet visited;
8176 bool memberInSection = cd->countMembersIncludingGrouped(lt,cd,FALSE)>0;
8177 bool show = (additionalList && !memberInSection) || // inherited member to show in the additional inherited members list
8178 (!additionalList && memberInSection); // inherited member to show in a member list of the class
8179 //printf("%s:%s show=%d\n",qPrint(cd->name()),qPrint(MemberList::listTypeAsString(lt)),show);
8180 if (show)
8181 {
8182 p->findInheritedMembers(cd,cd,lt,-1,title,additionalList,visited);
8183 }
8184}
8185
8186InheritedMemberInfoListContext::~InheritedMemberInfoListContext()
8187{
8188}
8189
8190// TemplateListIntf
8191size_t InheritedMemberInfoListContext::count() const
8192{
8193 return p->count();
8194}
8195
8196TemplateVariant InheritedMemberInfoListContext::at(size_t index) const
8197{
8198 return p->at(index);
8199}
8200
8201TemplateListIntf::ConstIteratorPtr InheritedMemberInfoListContext::createIterator() const
8202{
8203 return p->createIterator();
8204}

8208class ArgumentContext::Private
8209{
8210 public:
8211 Private(const Argument &arg,const Definition *def,const QCString &relPath)
8212 : m_argument(arg), m_def(def), m_relPath(relPath) {}
8213
8214 // TemplateStructIntf methods
8215 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
8216 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
8217
8218 private:
8219 // Property getters
8220 TemplateVariant type() const { return m_type.get(this); }
8221 TemplateVariant attrib() const { return m_argument.attrib; }
8222 TemplateVariant name() const { return m_argument.name; }
8223 TemplateVariant defVal() const { return m_defval.get(this); }
8224 TemplateVariant array() const { return m_argument.array; }
8225 TemplateVariant docs() const { return m_docs.get(this); }
8226 TemplateVariant namePart() const
8227 {
8228 QCString result = m_argument.attrib;
8229 size_t l = result.length();
8230 if (l>2 && result.at(0)=='[' && result.at(l-1)==']')
8231 {
8232 result = result.mid(1,l-2);
8233 if (result!=",") result+=":"; // for normal keywords add colon
8234 }
8235 return result;
8236 }
8237
8238 private:
8239 TemplateVariant createType() const
8240 {
8241 return createLinkedText(m_def,m_relPath,m_argument.type);
8242 }
8243 TemplateVariant createDefval() const
8244 {
8245 return createLinkedText(m_def,m_relPath,m_argument.defval);
8246 }
8247 TemplateVariant createDocs() const
8248 {
8249 return !m_argument.docs.isEmpty() ?
8250 TemplateVariant(parseDoc(m_def,m_def->docFile(),m_def->docLine(),m_relPath,m_argument.docs,TRUE)) :
8251 TemplateVariant("");
8252 }
8253 Argument m_argument;
8254 const Definition *m_def;
8255 QCString m_relPath;
8256 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createType> m_type;
8257 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDefval> m_defval;
8258 CachedItem<TemplateVariant, Private, &Private::createDocs> m_docs;
8259 static const PropertyMap<ArgumentContext::Private> s_inst;
8260};
8261

8266 { "name", &Private::name },

8268 { "docs", &Private::docs },

8339//------------------------------------------------------------------------
8340
8341// SymbolIndex
8342// - name: string
8343// - letter: string
8344// - symbolGroups: SymbolGroupList
8345// SymbolGroupList: list of SymbolGroups
8346// SymbolGroup
8347// - id
8348// - name
8349// - symbols: SymbolList
8350// SymbolList: list of Symbols
8351// Symbol
8352// - obj
8353// - scope
8354// - relPath
8355
8356//------------------------------------------------------------------------
8357
8358class SymbolContext::Private
8359{
8360 public:
8361 Private(const Definition *d,const Definition *prev, const Definition *next)
8362 : m_def(d), m_prevDef(prev), m_nextDef(next) {}
8363
8364 // TemplateStructIntf methods
8365 TemplateVariant get(const QCString &n) const { return s_inst.get(this,n); }
8366 StringVector fields() const { return s_inst.fields(); }
8367
8368 private:
8369 // Property getters
8370 TemplateVariant fileName() const { return m_def->getOutputFileBase(); }
8371 TemplateVariant anchor() const { return m_def->anchor(); }
8372 TemplateVariant scope() const { return m_scope.get(this); }
8373 TemplateVariant relPath() const { return externalRef("../",m_def->getReference(),TRUE); }
8374
8375 private:
8376 TemplateVariant createScope() const
8377 {
8378 const Definition *scope = m_def->getOuterScope();
8379 const Definition *next = m_nextDef;
8380 const Definition *prev = m_prevDef;
8381 const Definition *nextScope = next ? next->getOuterScope() : 0;
8382 const Definition *prevScope = prev ? prev->getOuterScope() : 0;
8383 const MemberDef *md = toMemberDef(m_def);
8384 bool isFunctionLike = md && (md->isFunction() || md->isSlot() || md->isSignal());
8385 bool overloadedFunction = ((prevScope!=0 && scope==prevScope) || (scope && scope==nextScope)) &&
8386 md && (md->isFunction() || md->isSlot());
8387
8388 QCString name;
8389 if (prev==0 && next==0) // unique name
8390 {
8391 if (scope!=Doxygen::globalScope)
8392 {
8393 name = scope->name();
8394 }
8395 else if (md)
8396 {
8397 const FileDef *fd = md->getBodyDef();
8398 if (fd==0) fd = md->getFileDef();
8399 if (fd)
8400 {
8401 name = fd->localName();
8402 }
8403 }
8404 }
8405 else
8406 {
8407 QCString prefix;
8408 if (md) prefix=md->localName();
8409 if (overloadedFunction) // overloaded member function
8410 {
8411 prefix+=md->argsString();
8412 // show argument list to disambiguate overloaded functions
8413 }
8414 else if (md && isFunctionLike) // unique member function
8415 {
8416 prefix+="()"; // only to show it is a function
8417 }
8418 bool found=FALSE;
8419 if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeClass)
8420 {
8421 name = m_def->displayName();
8422 found = TRUE;
8423 }
8424 else if (m_def->definitionType()==Definition::TypeNamespace)
8425 {
8426 name = m_def->displayName();
8427 found = TRUE;
8428 }
8429 else if (scope==0 || scope==Doxygen::globalScope) // in global scope
8430 {
8431 if (md)
8432 {
8433 const FileDef *fd = md->getBodyDef();
8434 if (fd==0) fd = md->getFileDef();
8435 if (fd)
8436 {
8437 if (!prefix.isEmpty()) prefix+=": ";
8438 name = prefix + convertToXML(fd->localName());
8439 found = TRUE;
8440 }
8441 }
8442 }
8443 else if (md && (md->resolveAlias()->getClassDef() || md->resolveAlias()->getNamespaceDef()))
8444 // member in class or namespace scope
8445 {
8446 SrcLangExt lang = md->getLanguage();
8447 name = m_def->getOuterScope()->qualifiedName()
8448 + getLanguageSpecificSeparator(lang) + prefix;
8449 found = TRUE;
8450 }
8451 else if (scope) // some thing else? -> show scope
8452 {
8453 name = prefix + convertToXML(scope->name());
8454 found = TRUE;
8455 }
8456 if (!found) // fallback
8457 {
8458 name = prefix + "("+theTranslator->trGlobalNamespace()+")";
8459 }
8460 }
8461 return name;
8462 }
8463 const Definition *m_def;
8464 const Definition *m_prevDef;
8465 const Definition *m_nextDef;
8466 CachedItem<TemplateVariant,Private,&Private::createScope> m_scope;
8467 static const PropertyMap<SymbolContext::Private> s_inst;
8468};
8469
8470//%% struct Symbol: specific search item
8471//%% {
8472const PropertyMap<SymbolContext::Private> SymbolContext::Private::s_inst {
8473 { "fileName",&Private::fileName },
8474 { "anchor", &Private::anchor },
8475 { "scope", &Private::scope },
8476 { "relPath", &Private::relPath }
8477};
8478//%% }
8479
8480SymbolContext::SymbolContext(const Definition *def,const Definition *prevDef,const Definition *nextDef) : p(std::make_unique<Private>(def,prevDef,nextDef))
8481{
8482}
8483
8484SymbolContext::~SymbolContext()
8485{

8489{
8490 return p->get(name);

8605//%% list SymbolGroupList[SymbolGroup] : list of search groups one per by name
8606class SymbolGroupListContext::Private : public GenericNodeListContext
8607{
8608 public:
8609 Private(const SearchIndexList &sil)
8610 {
8611 QCString lastName;
8612 auto it = sil.begin();
8613 auto it_begin = it;
8614 while (it!=sil.end())
8615 {
8616 QCString name = searchName(*it);
8617 if (name!=lastName)
8618 {
8619 if (it!=it_begin)
8620 {
8621 append(SymbolGroupContext::alloc(it_begin,it));
8622 }
8623 it_begin = it;
8624 lastName = name;
8625 }
8626 ++it;
8627 }
8628 if (it_begin!=sil.end())
8629 {
8630 append(SymbolGroupContext::alloc(it_begin,sil.end()));
8631 }
8632 }
8633};
8634
8635SymbolGroupListContext::SymbolGroupListContext(const SearchIndexList &sil) : p(std::make_unique<Private>(sil))
8636{
8637}
8638
8639SymbolGroupListContext::~SymbolGroupListContext()
8640{
8641}

8646 return p->count();

8869
8870class LatexSpaceless : public TemplateSpacelessIntf
8871{
8872 public:
8873 LatexSpaceless() { reset(); }
8874 std::unique_ptr<TemplateSpacelessIntf> clone()
8875 {
8876 return std::make_unique<LatexSpaceless>(*this);
8877 }
8878 void reset() { }
8879 QCString remove(const QCString &s)
8880 {
8881 if (s.isEmpty()) return s;
8882 TextStream result;
8883 const char *p = s.data();
8884 char c;
8885 while ((c=*p++))
8886 {
8887 switch(c)
8888 {
8889 case '\t': case ' ': case '\n':
8890 break;
8891 default:
8892 result << c;
8893 break;
8894 }
8895 }
8896 return result.str();
8897 }
8898 private:
8899};
8900
8901//------------------------------------------------------------------------
8902
8903class HtmlSpaceless : public TemplateSpacelessIntf
8904{
8905 public:
8906 HtmlSpaceless() { reset(); }
8907 std::unique_ptr<TemplateSpacelessIntf> clone()
8908 {
8909 return std::make_unique<HtmlSpaceless>(*this);
8910 }
8911 void reset()
8912 {
8913 m_insideTag = FALSE;
8914 m_insideString = '\0';
8915 m_removeSpaces = TRUE;
8916 }
8917 QCString remove(const QCString &s)
8918 {
8919 if (s.isEmpty()) return s;
8920 TextStream result;
8921 const char *p = s.data();
8922 char c;
8923 while ((c=*p++))
8924 {
8925 switch(c)
8926 {
8927 case '<': // start of a tag
8928 if (!m_insideString) m_insideTag=TRUE,m_removeSpaces=FALSE;
8929 result << c;
8930 break;
8931 case '>': // end of a tag
8932 if (!m_insideString) m_insideTag=FALSE,m_removeSpaces=TRUE;
8933 result << c;
8934 break;
8935 case '\\': // escaped character in a string
8936 result << c;
8937 if (m_insideString && *p) result << *p++;
8938 break;
8939 case '"': case '\'':
8940 if (m_insideTag)
8941 {
8942 if (m_insideString==c) // end of string
8943 {
8944 m_insideString='\0';
8945 }
8946 else if (m_insideString=='\0') // start of string
8947 {
8948 m_insideString=c;
8949 }
8950 }
8951 result << c;
8952 break;
8953 case ' ': case '\t': case '\n': // whitespace
8954 if (!m_insideTag) // outside tags strip consecutive whitespace
8955 {
8956 m_removeSpaces=TRUE;
8957 }
8958 else
8959 {
8960 result << ' ';
8961 }
8962 break;
8963 default:
8964 //if (m_removeSpaces) result+=' ';
8965 result << c;
8966 m_removeSpaces=FALSE;
8967 break;
8968 }
8969 }
8970 //printf("HtmlSpaceless::remove({%s})={%s} m_insideTag=%d m_insideString=%c (%d) removeSpaces=%d\n",qPrint(s),qPrint(result),
8971 // m_insideTag,m_insideString,m_insideString,m_removeSpaces);
8972 return result.str();
8973 }
8974 private:
8975 bool m_insideTag;
8976 char m_insideString;
8977 bool m_removeSpaces;
8978};
8979
8980//------------------------------------------------------------------------

9001
9002void generateOutputViaTemplate()
9003{
9004 {
9005 auto e = std::make_unique<TemplateEngine>();
9006 auto ctx = e->createContext();
9007 if (ctx)
9008 {
9009 TemplateStructIntfPtr doxygen (DoxygenContext::alloc());
9010 TemplateStructIntfPtr config (ConfigContext::alloc());
9011 TemplateStructIntfPtr tr (TranslateContext::alloc());
9012 TemplateListIntfPtr classList (ClassListContext::alloc());
9013 TemplateStructIntfPtr classIndex (ClassIndexContext::alloc());
9014 TemplateStructIntfPtr classTree (ClassTreeContext::alloc());
9015 TemplateStructIntfPtr classHierarchy (ClassHierarchyContext::alloc());
9016 TemplateListIntfPtr conceptList (ConceptListContext::alloc());
9017 TemplateStructIntfPtr conceptTree (ConceptTreeContext::alloc());
9018 TemplateListIntfPtr namespaceList (NamespaceListContext::alloc());
9019 TemplateStructIntfPtr namespaceTree (NamespaceTreeContext::alloc());
9020 TemplateListIntfPtr dirList (DirListContext::alloc());
9021 TemplateListIntfPtr fileList (FileListContext::alloc());
9022 TemplateStructIntfPtr fileTree (FileTreeContext::alloc());
9023 TemplateStructIntfPtr pageTree (PageTreeContext::alloc(*Doxygen::pageLinkedMap));
9024 TemplateListIntfPtr pageList (PageListContext::alloc(*Doxygen::pageLinkedMap));
9025 TemplateStructIntfPtr exampleTree (ExampleTreeContext::alloc());
9026 TemplateListIntfPtr exampleList (ExampleListContext::alloc());
9027 TemplateStructIntfPtr moduleTree (ModuleTreeContext::alloc());
9028 TemplateListIntfPtr moduleList (ModuleListContext::alloc());
9029 TemplateStructIntfPtr globalsIndex (GlobalsIndexContext::alloc());
9030 TemplateStructIntfPtr classMembersIndex (ClassMembersIndexContext::alloc());
9031 TemplateStructIntfPtr namespaceMembersIndex(NamespaceMembersIndexContext::alloc());
9032 TemplateListIntfPtr searchIndices (SearchIndicesContext::alloc());
9033
9034 //%% Doxygen doxygen:
9035 ctx->set("doxygen",doxygen);
9036 //%% Translator tr:
9037 ctx->set("tr",tr);
9038 //%% Config config:
9039 ctx->set("config",config);
9040 //%% ClassList classList:
9041 ctx->set("classList",classList); // not used for standard HTML
9042 //%% ClassTree classTree:
9043 ctx->set("classTree",classTree);
9044 //%% ClassIndex classIndex:
9045 ctx->set("classIndex",classIndex);
9046 //%% ClassHierarchy classHierarchy:
9047 ctx->set("classHierarchy",classHierarchy);
9048 //%% ConceptList conceptList:
9049 ctx->set("conceptList",conceptList);
9050 //%% ConceptTree conceptTree:
9051 ctx->set("conceptTree",conceptTree);
9052 //%% NamespaceList namespaceList:
9053 ctx->set("namespaceList",namespaceList);
9054 //%% NamespaceTree namespaceTree:
9055 ctx->set("namespaceTree",namespaceTree);
9056 //%% FileList fileList:
9057 ctx->set("fileList",fileList);
9058 //%% FileTree fileTree:
9059 ctx->set("fileTree",fileTree);
9060 //%% PageList pageList
9061 ctx->set("pageList",pageList);
9062 //%% PageTree pageTree
9063 ctx->set("pageTree",pageTree);
9064 //%% ExampleTree exampleTree
9065 ctx->set("exampleTree",exampleTree);
9066 //%% ExampleList exampleList
9067 ctx->set("exampleList",exampleList);
9068 //%% ModuleTree moduleTree
9069 ctx->set("moduleTree",moduleTree);
9070 //%% ModuleList moduleList
9071 ctx->set("moduleList",moduleList);
9072 //%% DirList dirList
9073 ctx->set("dirList",dirList);
9074 //%% Page mainPage
9075 if (Doxygen::mainPage)
9076 {
9077 TemplateStructIntfPtr mainPage = PageContext::alloc(Doxygen::mainPage.get(),TRUE,FALSE);
9078 ctx->set("mainPage",mainPage);
9079 }
9080 else
9081 {
9082 // TODO: for LaTeX output index should be main... => solve in template
9083 Doxygen::mainPage.reset(createPageDef("[generated]",1,"index","",Config_getString(PROJECT_NAME)));
9084 Doxygen::mainPage->setFileName("index");
9085 TemplateStructIntfPtr mainPage = PageContext::alloc(Doxygen::mainPage.get(),TRUE,FALSE);
9086 ctx->set("mainPage",mainPage);
9087 }
9088 //%% GlobalsIndex globalsIndex:
9089 ctx->set("globalsIndex",globalsIndex);
9090 //%% ClassMembersIndex classMembersIndex:
9091 ctx->set("classMembersIndex",classMembersIndex);
9092 //%% NamespaceMembersIndex namespaceMembersIndex:
9093 ctx->set("namespaceMembersIndex",namespaceMembersIndex);
9094 //%% SearchIndices searchIndices
9095 ctx->set("searchIndices",searchIndices);
9096 //%% string space
9097 ctx->set("space"," ");
9098
9099 //if (Config_getBool(GENERATE_HTML))
9100 { // render HTML output
9101 e->setTemplateDir("templates/html"); // TODO: make template part user configurable
9102 Template *tpl = e->loadByName("htmllayout.tpl",1);
9103 if (tpl)
9104 {
9105 g_globals.outputFormat = ContextOutputFormat_Html;
9106 g_globals.dynSectionId = 0;
9107 g_globals.outputDir = Config_getString(HTML_OUTPUT);
9108 Dir dir(g_globals.outputDir.str());
9109 createSubDirs(dir);
9110 ctx->setEscapeIntf(Config_getString(HTML_FILE_EXTENSION),std::make_unique<HtmlEscaper>());
9111 ctx->setSpacelessIntf(std::make_unique<HtmlSpaceless>());
9112 ctx->setOutputDirectory(g_globals.outputDir);
9113 TextStream ts;
9114 tpl->render(ts,ctx.get());
9115 }
9116 e->unload(tpl);
9117 }
9118
9119 // TODO: clean index before each run...
9120
9121 //if (Config_getBool(GENERATE_LATEX))
9122 if (0)
9123 { // render LaTeX output
9124 e->setTemplateDir("templates/latex"); // TODO: make template part user configurable
9125 Template *tpl = e->loadByName("latexlayout.tpl",1);
9126 if (tpl)
9127 {
9128 g_globals.outputFormat = ContextOutputFormat_Latex;
9129 g_globals.dynSectionId = 0;
9130 g_globals.outputDir = Config_getString(LATEX_OUTPUT);
9131 Dir dir(g_globals.outputDir.str());
9132 createSubDirs(dir);
9133 ctx->setEscapeIntf(".tex",std::make_unique<LatexEscaper>());
9134 ctx->setSpacelessIntf(std::make_unique<LatexSpaceless>());
9135 ctx->setOutputDirectory(g_globals.outputDir);
9136 TextStream ts;
9137 tpl->render(ts,ctx.get());
9138 }
9139 e->unload(tpl);
9140 }
9141 }
9142 }
9143}
9144
9145void generateTemplateFiles(const QCString &templateDir)
9146{
9147 if (templateDir.isEmpty()) return;
9148 Dir thisDir;
9149 if (!thisDir.exists(templateDir.str()) && !thisDir.mkdir(templateDir.str()))
9150 {
9151 err("Failed to create output directory '%s'\n",qPrint(templateDir));
9152 return;
9153 }
9154 std::string outDir = templateDir.str()+"/html";
9155 if (!thisDir.exists(outDir) && !thisDir.mkdir(outDir))
9156 {
9157 err("Failed to create output directory '%s'\n",outDir.c_str());
9158 return;
9159 }
9160 ResourceMgr::instance().writeCategory("html",outDir.c_str());
9161}
